C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyourbestcreditcards.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYourBestCreditCards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aim%20to%20help%20people%20choose%20what%20cards%20to%20use%20and%20how%20to%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20having%20dinner%20with%20me%2C%20I'm%20always%20going%20to%20judge%20what%20card%20you%20pay%20with.%20The%20US%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20countries%20where%20you%20can%20collect%20miles%2C%20but%20people%20just%20aren't%20maximizing%20benefits%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20I'd%20like%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20seven%20worst%20credit%20card%20mistakes%20I%20see%20people%20make%2C%20but%20you%20can%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Choosing%20a%20rewards%20credit%20card%20when%20they%20can't%20pay%20their%20balance%20in%20full%20each%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERewards%20cards%20are%20great%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20carry%20a%20balance%2C%20they%20are%20your%20worst%20choice%20as%20they%20have%20the%20highest%20annual%20percentage%20rates%20(APR)%20of%20any%20card%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20you%2C%20choose%20a%20card%20with%20a%200%25%20APR%20intro%20or%20a%20Balance%20Transfer%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20your%20balances%20down%20to%20zero%2C%20and%20promise%20yourself%20not%20to%20charge%20anything%20you%20can't%20pay%20in%20full.%20Then%2C%20you%20can%20get%20a%20rewards%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Putting%20all%20of%20their%20charges%20on%20an%20airline%20or%20hotel-branded%20credit%20card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20those%20cards%20can%20come%20with%20great%20benefits%2C%20they're%20rarely%20your%20best%20choice%20for%20day-to-day%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20be%20tied%20to%20the%20whims%20of%20that%20one%20program%2C%20meaning%20you'll%20be%20stuck%20with%20whatever%20devaluations%20this%20one%20brand%20introduces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22