tage%20situation%20is%20unfolding%20at%20the%20address%20of%20the%20swatter's%20intended%20victim.%20Typically%2C%20a%20heavily%20armed%20SWAT%20team%20will%20show%20up%20at%20the%20unwitting%20victim's%20home%20and%20burst%20through%20the%20door%2C%20guns%20drawn.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffatal-call-of-duty-swatting-incident-20-years-sentence-convicted-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESometimes%2C%20the%20outcome%20is%20deadly%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20swatting%20victims%20have%20included%20Republicans%20including%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%20of%20Georgia%2C%20Sen.%20Rick%20Scott%20of%20Florida%2C%20and%20Ohio%20Attorney%20General%20Dave%20Yost.%20Democrats%20have%20not%20gone%20unscathed%2C%20either%20%E2%80%94%20Boston%20Mayor%20Michelle%20Wu%20was%20swatted%20on%20Christmas%20Day.%20Multiple%20officials%20in%20Georgia%2C%20including%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20and%20at%20least%20four%20state%20senators%2C%20also%20reported%20being%20swatted%20within%20the%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ajc.com%2Fnews%2Fswatting-calls-target-politicians-in-georgia-and-across-the-nation%2FX5REZNXNXVBBRPS4SVJODZE63A%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Atlanta%20Journal-Constitution%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreene%20even%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20both%20of%20her%20two%20daughters'%20homes%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMTG%2Fstatus%2F1740461050900681196%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeted%20by%20swatting%20attempts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20December%2028.%20On%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20Greene%20wrote%20that%20she%20has%20been%20personally%20swatted%20approximately%20eight%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20FBI%20has%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20'phenomenon'%20of%20swatting%20since%20at%20least%202008%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%201%2C000%20swatting%20incidents%20occur%20across%20the%20United%20States%20each%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Kevin%20Kolbye%2C%20a%20former%20FBI%20assistant%20special%20agent%20who%20investigated%20swatting%20crimes.%20Kolbye%2C%20who%20died%20in%20October%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%202017%20interview%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpolice-solutions-swatting-prank-calls-2020-10%3F_gl%3D1*mq23lh*_ga*MTgyNTk4MDA4Ny4xNjk5NDYxODAz*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwMzg1OTI5NC45My4xLjE3MDM4NjAwOTcuNDYuMC4w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswatters%20are%20often%20difficult%20to%20trace%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20mask%20their%20identities%20and%20use%20falsified%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKolbye%20said%20police%20are%20often%20unable%20to%20distinguish%20between%20a%20swatting%20call%20and%20a%20true%20emergency%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20because%20the%20crimes%20being%20reported%20are%20so%20severe%20that%20police%20are%20forced%20to%20react%20swiftly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20information%20is%20going%20out%2C%20police%20and%20SWAT%20teams%20are%20rolling%20out%20to%20these%20things%20thinking%20they've%20got%20a%20real-life%20crisis%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Kolbye%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20first%20drew%20public%20attention%20to%20swatting%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchives.fbi.gov%2Farchives%2Fnews%2Fstories%2F2008%2Ffebruary%2Fswatting020408%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20calling%20the%20practice%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20phenomenon%26quot%3B%20of%20increasing%20concern%20to%20local%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20community%20is%20placed%20in%20danger%20as%20responders%20rush%20to%20the%20scene%2C%20taking%20them%20away%20from%20real%20emergencies.%20And%20the%20officers%20are%20placed%20in%20danger%20as%20unsuspecting%20residents%20may%20try%20to%20defend%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FBI%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESwatting%20has%20turned%20deadly%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20residents%2C%20too%2C%20face%20immense%20risk%20when%20the%20SWAT%20teams%20arrive.%20As%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20Wichita%20man%2C%20Andrew%20Finch%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpolice-solutions-swatting-prank-calls-2020-10%3F_gl%3D1*mq23lh*_ga*MTgyNTk4MDA4Ny4xNjk5NDYxODAz*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwMzg1OTI5NC45My4xLjE3MDM4NjAwOTcuNDYuMC4w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekilled%20by%20police%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20they%20arrived%20at%20his%20door%20due%20to%20a%20swatting%20call.%20In%202020%2C%20another%20swatting%20victim%2C%20Mark%20Herring%2C%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20after%20heavily%20armed%20cops%20converged%20on%20his%20Tennessee%20home.%20His%20daughter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Ftennessee-man-targeted-his-twitter-handle-dies-after-swatting-call-n1274747%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20believes%20Herring%20was%20%26quot%3Bscared%20to%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20perpetrators%20involved%20in%20the%20swattings%20were%20caught%20and%20sent%20to%20prison.%20Finch's%20swatter%2C%20Tyler%20Barris%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%2020%20years%20in%20federal%20prison%2C%20and%20one%20of%20Herring's%20swatters%2C%20Shane%20Sonderman%2C%20received%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20oftentimes%2C%20swatters%20use%20temporary%20burner%20phone%20numbers%20and%20voice%20changers.%20So%20far%2C%20amid%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20swattings%20against%20lawmakers%2C%20authorities%20have%20not%20publicly%20identified%20any%20suspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20tackle%20combat%20swatting%20incidents%20nationwide%2C%20the%20FBI%20announced%20in%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Ffbi-formed-national-database-track-prevent-swatting-rcna91722%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20national%20online%20database%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20allow%20hundreds%20of%20police%20departments%20and%20law-enforcement%20agencies%20to%20share%20information%20about%20swatting%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStates%20including%20Ohio%20and%20Virginia%20have%20also%20recently%20implemented%20stronger%20laws%20against%20swatting%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Ohio%20made%20swatting%20a%20felony%20this%20year%2C%20and%20Virginia%20bumped%20up%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20for%20swatting%20to%2012%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fswatting-calls-marjorie-taylor-greene-rick-scott-d568818925c99c8cf17467f737b99e97%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20Georgia%20state%20senator%2C%20Clint%20Dixon%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsenatepress.net%2Fsen-clint-dixon-condemns-swatting-calls.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20will%20introduce%20legislation%20in%202024%20to%20mandate%20harsher%20penalties%20for%20false%20reporting%20and%20misuse%20of%20police%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20goes%20beyond%20politics%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20public%20safety%20and%20preserving%20the%20integrity%20of%20our%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20Dixon%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20stand%20for%20these%20threats%20of%20violence%20and%20intimidation.%20Those%20involved%20in%20swatting%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20under%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreene%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMTG%2Fstatus%2F1739390262378377575%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20would%20introduce%20federal%20legislation%20to%20%26quot%3Btrack%20down%20swatters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-spate-of-recent-swatting-incidents-has-targeted-republican-lawmakers-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa