feet%20%E2%80%94%20are%20set%20to%20open%20in%202024%20and%202025.%20Beyond%20that%20timeframe%2C%20there%20are%20few%20projects%20on%20the%20horizon%20that%20would%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20higher%20construction%20costs%20and%20heightened%20office%20vacancy%20rates%2C%20areas%20like%20Midtown%20Manhattan%20and%20Lower%20Manhattan%2C%20which%20have%20long%20been%20the%20nexus%20of%20operations%20for%20influential%20companies%2C%20are%20set%20to%20see%20a%20slowdown%20in%20the%20proliferation%20of%20large%20office%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20nearly%2020%20large%20office%20buildings%20proposed%20for%20construction%20have%20yet%20to%20see%20shovels%20in%20the%20ground%20to%20kick%20off%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20issue%20of%20signing%20anchor%20tenants%20to%20commit%20to%20occupying%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20square%20feet%20of%20office%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20final%20centerpieces%20of%20the%20new%20World%20Trade%20Center%20complex%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F9-11-anniversary-world-trade-center-rebuilding-larry-silverstein-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20long-planned%202%20World%20Trade%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20yet%20to%20commence%20construction%20as%20developer%20Silverstein%20Properties%20has%20so%20far%20been%20unable%20to%20find%20an%20anchor%20tenant%20for%20the%20building%2C%20per%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20developers%20looking%20to%20sign%20a%20tenant%20to%20a%20large%20building%2C%20the%20market%20is%20simply%20not%20seeing%20large%20employers%20looking%20to%20move%20from%20their%20current%20spaces%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226465%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WTC%20complex%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c