ives%20for%20Lythgoe%20and%20Nigel%20Lythgoe%20Productions%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20made%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Derulo%2C%20Paula%20Abdul%2C%20and%20Nigel%20Lythgoe%20on%20%26quot%3BSo%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance%26quot%3B%20in%20March%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65903144ec62ab5daf7fc6b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Derulo%2C%20Paula%20Abdul%2C%20and%20Nigel%20Lythgoe%20on%20%26quot%3BSo%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance%26quot%3B%20in%20March%202016.%3Cp%3EFOX%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Abdul's%20attorney%2C%20Douglas%20Johnson%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%20lauding%20his%20client%20for%20coming%20forward%20with%20her%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Abdul%20should%20be%20commended%20for%20the%20immense%20courage%20required%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20type%20of%20abuse%20that%20was%20inflicted%20upon%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20when%20the%20alleged%20abuser%20is%20a%20figure%20so%20dominant%20in%20her%20profession.%20It%20was%20clearly%20a%20difficult%20decision%20to%20make%2C%20but%20Ms.%20Abdul%20knows%20that%20she%20stands%20both%20in%20the%20shoes%20and%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20many%20other%20similarly%20situated%20survivors%2C%20and%20she%20is%20determined%20to%20see%20that%20justice%20is%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20suit%2C%20Abdul%20accused%20Lythgoe%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20her%20a%20second%20time%20years%20later%2C%20when%20Abdul%20served%20as%20a%20judge%20on%20%26quot%3BSo%20You%20Think%20You%20Can%20Dance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbdul%20alleged%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20Lythgoe%20invited%20he