E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Australian%20envoy%20Philip%20Green%20lauded%20the%20India-Australia%20relationship%2C%20which%20is%20at%20its%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20point%26quot%3B%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAffirming%20his%20dedication%20to%20advancing%20the%20partnership%20between%20the%20countries%2C%20he%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20further%20propel%20the%20relationship%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20relationship%20is%20at%20the%20highest%20point%20in%20our%20history.%20But%20I'm%20not%20here%20to%20rest%20on%20laurels.%20I'm%20here%20to%20get%20more%20things%20done.%20I'm%20here%20to%20drive%20the%20relationship%20further%20and%20to%20drive%20it%20faster.%20That's%20what%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20told%20me%20to%20do%20when%20he%20sent%20me%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20envoy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20India's%20paramount%20significance%20in%20their%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20he%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20proactive%20engagement%20during%20his%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20our%20two-way%20trade%20has%20grown%20by%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20And%20last%20year%2C%20we%20signed%20the%20landmark%20Economic%20Cooperation%20and%20Trade%20Agreement%20(ECTA).%20This%20deal%20has%20provided%20the%20momentum%20for%20negotiations%20towards%20an%20even%20more%20ambitious%20goal%3A%20a%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Cooperation%20Agreement%20or%20CECA%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20and%20Australia%20have%20also%20implemented%20an%20economic%20cooperation%20and%20trade%20agreement%20(ECTA)%20and%20are%20now%20negotiating%20the%20expansion%20of%20its%20scope%20for%20the%20CECA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Australia%20Economic%20Cooperation%20and%20Trade%20Agreement%20(IndAusECTA)%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20December%2029%2C%202022.%20The%20ECTA%20was%20signed%20on%20April%202%2C%20