ngagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpakhawaj-maestro-pandit-bhavani-shankar-passes-away-due-to-cardiac-arrest%2Farticleshow%2F106407388.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20To%20Pen%20New%20Year%20'POEM'%20In%20Space%2C%20Creating%20%26quot%3BWealth%20From%20Waste%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20launches%20its%20specialised%20observatory%20to%20study%20neutron%20stars%20and%20black%20holes%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%20on%20Monday%2C%20it%20will%20also%20send%20a%20'POEM'%20up%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'PSLV%20Orbital%20Experimental%20Module'%2C%20or%20POEM%2C%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20which%20will%20undertake%20its%2060th%20flight%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-conquering-moon-india-turns-its-attention-to-black-holes-4769567%5C%22%3Ecarry%20the%20XPoSAT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20the%20X-ray%20Polarimeter%20Satellite%20as%20its%20primary%20payload.%20The%20POEM%20will%20have%2010%20experiments%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20which%20will%20be%20a%20'Women%20Engineered%20Satellite'%20(WESAT)%20made%20by%20an%20institute%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20flight%20of%20POEM%2C%20which%20can%20easily%20be%20described%20as%20a%20low-cost%2C%20non-human%20Indian%20space%20station.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20creating%20wealth%20from%20waste%20in%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20S%20Somanath%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20space%20agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%2C%20during%20earlier%20missions%2C%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20the%20PSLV%20was%20left%20to%20burn%20up%20in%20space%20and%20create%20space%20debris%2C%20but%20it%20is%20now%20being%20used%20as%20a%20resource%2C%20and%20high-value%20experiments%20are%20being%20undertaken.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20experiments%20on%20POEM%20are%20by%20Indian%20startups%20and%20others%20by%20ISRO%20to%20test%20and%20validate%20space%20technologies%2C%20using%20the%20spent%20fourth%20stage%20to%20carry%20out%20in-orbit%20scientific%20experiments%20for%20an%20extended%20duration%20of%20one%20to%20six%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudent%20'Satellite'%2C%20Green%20Experiment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2010%20experiments%20is%20a%20'Women%20Engineered%20Satellite'%20(WESAT)%20made%20by%20the%20LBS%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20for%20Women%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20which%20has%20been%20put%20together%20thanks%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20Dr%20Lizy%20Abraham%2C%20the%20principal%20investigator%20for%20the%20project.%20Sheril%20Mariam%20Jose%2C%20student%20coordinator%20for%20WESAT%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20mission%20holds%20a%20special%20significance%20as%20it%20marks%20the%20first-ever%20women-led%2C%20women-only%20satellite%20of%20India%20and%20it%20is%20also%20the%20first%20student%20satellite%20from%20Kerala.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20pointed%20out%20that%20calling%20WESAT%20a%20%60satellite'%20is%20a%20misnomer%20as%20it%20is%20merely%20a%20%60payload'%20onboard%20the%20POEM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20established%20space%20startup%2C%20Bellatrix%20Aerospace%20Limited%2C%20is%20flying%20two%20payload%20experiments%20which%20include%20the%20use%20of%20a%20green%20monopropellant%20thruster.%20The%20world%20is%20working%20towards%20using%20rocket%20fuels%20that%20are%20less%20toxic%20and%20this%20startup%2C%20incubated%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20aims%20to%20make%20rocket%20launches%20environment-friendly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhruva%20Aerospace%20Private%20Limited%20is%20flying%20experiments%20related%20to%20microsatellites%20in%20line%20with%20its%20motto%3A%20'Creating%20exceptional%20small%20satellite%20systems%20to%20help%20space%20exploration%20technology%20meet%20human%20imagination%20and%20innovation'.%20Microsatellites%20are%20very%20promising%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20world%20is%20trying%20to%20set%20up%20constellations%20of%20thousands%20of%20satellites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20(VSSC)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20ISRO%2C%20is%20flying%20two%20experiments%20-%20%C2%A0a%20fuel%20cell%20power%20system%20and%20a%20high-energy%20cell.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20partners%20on%20POEM%20are%20trying%20to%20exploit%20the%20unique%20space-based%20low-cost%20resource%20made%20available%20by%20the%20Indian%20space%20agency.%20%26quot%3BISRO%20is%20opening%20its%20doors%20wider%20than%20ever%20to%20private-sector%20participation%20so%20that%2C%20together%2C%20it%20can%20successfully%20boost%20the%20space%20economy%20for%20a%20resurgent%20%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(self-reliant)%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Pawan%20Goenka%2C%20Chairman%2C%20Indian%20National%20Space%20Promotion%20and%20Authorization%20Centre%20(IN-SPACe).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20assessment%20by%20IN-SPACe%20suggests%20that%20the%20Indian%20space%20economy%20is%20valued%20at%20around%20%248%20billion%2C%20with%20a%202%25%20share%20in%20the%20global%20space%20economy.%20It%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20reach%20%2444%20billion%20by%202033%2C%20with%20about%208%25%20of%20the%20global%20share.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrbit%20Injection%2C%20Lowering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20after%20the%20injection%20of%20XPoSat%20at%20650%20km%2C%20the%20fourth%20stage%20(PS4)%20of%20PSLV%20will%20be%20lowered%20to%20a%20350-km%20orbit%20by%20restarting%20it%20twice.%20The%20leftover%20propellant%20in%20the%20module%20will%20be%20disposed%20of%20through%20the%20main%20engines%20as%20a%20precursor%20to%20enabling%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20PS4%20stage%20in%20atmospheric%20re-entry%20experiments%20planned%20in%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20oxidiser%20will%20be%20let%20out%20first%2C%20followed%20by%20fuel%20in%20a%20predetermined%20sequence%20of%20operations.%20The%20existing%20scheme%20of%20spent%20stage%20passivation%20by%20venting%20the%20tank%20pressure%20will%20also%20be%20active.%20After%20the%20passivation%20of%20PS4%2C%20the%20control%20of%20the%20stage%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20avionics%20on%20board%20the%20POEM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PS4%20is%20configured%20as%20a%20three-axis%20stabilised%20orbital%20platform%20for%20conducting%20experiments%20to%20space-qualify%20systems%20with%20novel%20ideas.%20The%20platform's%20electrical%20power%20requirements%20are%20met%20by%20flexible%20solar%20panels%20in%20conjunction%20with%20a%20lithium-ion%20battery%20The%20orbital%20platform%20consists%20of%20avionic%20systems%20to%20take%20care%20of%20navigation%2C%20guidance%2C%20control%20and%20tele-commands%20and%20an%20orbital%20platform%20attitude%20control%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20low-cost%2C%20high-value%20opportunities%20are%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20give%20a%20catalytic%20boost%20to%20the%20Indian%20space%20ecosystem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrand%20Ambition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20grander%20scale%2C%20India%20is%20aiming%20to%20set%20up%20a%20full-fledged%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20(BAS)%20by%202035%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20According%20to%20ISRO%2C%20the%20BAS%20will%20weigh%20about%2025%20tonnes%20and%20will%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bgateway%20for%20interplanetary%20missions%26quot%3B.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20used%20for%20micro-gravity%20studies%20and%20experiments%20on%20space%20biology%20and%20space%20medicine.%20Mr%20Somanath%20asserted%20that%20India%20will%20have%20a%20sustained%20presence%20in%20space%20by%202035%20through%20an%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Batmanirbhar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20effort.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703949720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdu6gecg_pslv-rocket_650x400_02_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launch-isro-xposat-launch-isro-to-pen-new-year-poem-in-space-creating-wealth-from-waste-4771013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20India%20launches%20its%20specialised%20observatory%20to%20study%20neutron%20stars%20and%20black%20holes%20on%20New%20Year's%20Day%20on%20Monday%2C%20it%20will%20also%20send%20a%20'POEM'%20up%20into%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launch-isro-xposat-launch-isro-to-pen-new-year-poem-in-space-creating-wealth-from-waste-4771013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launch-isro-xposat-launch-isro-to-pen-new-year-poem-in-space-creating-wealth-from-waste-4771013%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-launch-isro-xposat-launch-isro-to-pen-new-year-poem-in-space-creating-wealth-from-waste-4771013%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%2085%3A%20Airstrikes%20hit%20camps%20in%20central%20Gaza%20as%20US%20approves%20new%20weapons%20sales%20to%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703949416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106407194%2Cimgsize-1473653.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-hamas-war-day-85-airstrikes-hit-camps-in-central-gaza-as-biden-administration-approves-new-weapons-sales-to-israel%2Farticleshow%2F106407164.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106407164.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20warplanes%20strike%20Gaza%2