dache-taken-to-hospital-4770637%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-star-suffers-nasty-collision-with-teammate-during-match-vs-australia-complains-of-headache-taken-to-hospital-4770637%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-star-suffers-nasty-collision-with-teammate-during-match-vs-australia-complains-of-headache-taken-to-hospital-4770637%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'Historic'%20Peace%20Accord%20with%20ULFA%20Had%20Lost%20its%20Worth%20Even%20Before%20It%20Was%20Inked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30190015%2FEffect-48.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Historic!%C2%A0Thus%20far%2C%20all%20agreements%20that%20the%20Centre%20(be%20it%20of%20any%20party)%20has%20signed%20with%20an%20armed%20outfit%20in%20Northeast%20India%20have%20been%20termed%20either%20by%20the%20signatories%2C%20or%20their%20political%20backers%2C%20no%20less%20than%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20till%20they%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20nowhere%20near%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2029%2C%20signing%20the%20agreement%20with%20the%20Arabinda%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA)%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20quite%20predictably%20termed%20it%20too%20as%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20only%20time%20can%20tell%20how%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20is%20this%20agreement%3B%20also%2C%20if%20it%20is%20more%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20than%20the%20Assam%20accord%20delivered%20by%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201985%2C%20which%20this%20new%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20peace%20accord%E2%80%99%20signed%20by%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20even%20make%20a%20mention%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20Assam%2C%20since%20the%201990s%2C%20one%20has%20seen%20three%20%E2%80%98peace%20accords%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Bodoland%E2%80%99%20area%20itself%2C%20signed%20with%20various%20Union%20governments%20held%20by%20the%20two%20national%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Each%20was%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20till%20it%20was%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20one%2C%20signed%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202020%2C%20was%20also%20termed%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20by%20Shah.%20However%2C%20the%20All%20Bodo%20Students%20Union%20(ABSU)%20president%20Dipen%20Boro%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Famit-shah-historic-bodo-peace-accord-sign-assam-1640584-2020-01-27%5C%22%3Estated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kokrajhar%20on%20December%2029%20that%20the%20agreement%20has%20not%20been%20%E2%80%9Cimplemented%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit%20by%20the%20state%20and%20central%20(Modi)%20government%E2%80%9D%20and%20if%20not%20done%20soon%2C%20the%20outfit%20vows%20to%20start%20a%20%E2%80%98democratic%20movement%E2%80%99.%20The%20ability%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20ministry%20to%20prove%20that%20the%202020%20agreement%20was%20indeed%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20is%20already%20under%20a%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20history%20has%20shown%20over%20and%20again%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20crafting%20one%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20peace%20agreement%20or%20the%20other%20with%20groups%20spearheading%20armed%20movements%20across%20the%20Northeast%20(remember%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20Naga%20Framework%20Agreement%20from%202015%3F)%2C%20time%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20not%20only%20to%20reckon%20the%20transient%20nature%20of%20these%20pacts%20but%20to%20cognise%20the%20need%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20%E2%80%93%20once%20and%20for%20all%20%E2%80%93%20to%20this%20litany.%20Simply%20because%20these%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20nothing%20but%20hollow%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20efficacy%20in%20profiting%20the%20public%20in%20general%20and%20the%20community%20it%20is%20intended%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fulfa-faction-signs-peace-accord-with-centre-political-gimmick-says-opposition-in-assam%5C%22%3EULFA%20Faction%20Signs%20%E2%80%98Peace%20Accord%E2%80%99%20with%20Centre%3B%20%E2%80%98Political%20Gimmick%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Opposition%20in%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20must%20the%20Assamese%20public%20learn%20from%20the%20December%2029%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20moment%20scripted%20within%20closed%20doors%20in%20their%20name%3F%20Importantly%2C%20what%20must%20they%20do%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20march%20of%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20with%20some%20angry%20group%20or%20the%20other%20by%20%3Cem%3ENotun%20Dilli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(New%20Delhi)%20ends%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%20simple%3B%20history%20must%20be%20the%20teacher%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeneficiaries%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98peace%20accord%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20to%20the%20prescriptive%20part%2C%20it%20is%20helpful%20though%20to%20hold%20up%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20this%20latest%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20there%20are%20clearly%20three%20direct%20beneficiaries.%20One%20is%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20ULFA.%20Since%202008%2C%20its%20cadres%20have%20been%20waiting%20in%20designated%20camps%20(set%20up%20by%20the%20government)%20for%20their%20leaders%20to%20pull%20off%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre.%20So%20that%2C%20they%20can%20not%20only%20get%20a%20means%20of%20livelihood%20but%20also%20integrate%20back%20into%20society.%20However%2C%20with%20nothing%20in%20sight%2C%20waiting%20for%20years%20together%2C%20several%20of%20them%20had%20begun%20deserting%20those%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30122351%2FEffect-46-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20with%20Arabinda%20Rajkhowa%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Asom%20(ULFA).%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40AmitShah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20among%20those%20disillusioned%20with%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20had%20begun%20looking%20for%20employment%20on%20their%20own%2C%20some%20others%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20jungles%20to%20join%20the%20anti-talks%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20run%20by%20Paresh%20Barua%20from%20Myanmar.%20What%20needs%20highlighting%20here%20is%20that%20most%20of%20that%20lot%20are%20the%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20Assamese%20peasants.%20This%20upheaval%20within%20Assamese%20peasantry%20is%20huge%20considering%20Assam%20is%20an%20agricultural%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advent%20in%20North%20Block%20in%202014%2C%20the%20interlocutor%20appointed%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20talks%20with%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20had%20changed.%20It%20meant%20the%20talks%20had%20to%20begin%20afresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20that%20new%20interlocutor%20was%20shifted%20out%20too.%20These%20changes%20have%20certainly%20slowed%20down%20the%20process.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20the%20initial%20euphoria%20within%20the%20Assamese%20public%20and%20the%20intellectuals%20about%20the%20likelihood%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20Assam%20Accord%20(no%20more%20historic%20by%20then)%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20pact%20through%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20began%20to%20lose%20steam.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20December%2029%20agreement%20with%20New%20Delhi%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20its%20worth%20is%20already%20diminished.%20Nobody%20in%20Assam%20expected%20it%20to%20be%20truly%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slowdown%20of%20the%20peace%20process%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20to%20tire%20out%20those%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20table%20because%20it%20ended%20up%20benefitting%20the%20Centre.%20It%20was%20exhausting%20for%20the%20ULFA%20leaders%20to%20wait%20endlessly%20for%20Godot%20to%20arrive.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20which%20has%20at%20least%20a%20semblance%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20exit%20for%20them.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20with%20their%20dwindling%20bargaining%20chips%2C%20the%20ULFA%20leaders%20needed%20this%20agreement%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20more%20than%20New%20Delhi%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inherent%20pressure%20on%20them%20to%20conclude%20a%20process%20that%20they%20had%20started%20with%20the%20Centre%20in%202011%20ensured%20that%20their%20stakes%20to%20sign%20on%20the%20dotted%20line%20were%20certainly%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20the%20Centre.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Assamese%20public%20looked%20on%2C%20with%20mixed%20feelings.%20Whether%20to%20expect%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%2C%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20no%20government%20(read%20party)%20will%20show%20any%20generosity%20to%20a%20militant%20group%20unless%20it%20looks%20at%20it%20as%20a%20milcher.%20It%20is%20particularly%20true%20with%20the%20Modi-era%20BJP.%20The%20timing%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20must%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20prime%20mover%20for%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Here%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20most%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20of%20the%20state%20are%20in%20Upper%20Assam%2C%20the%20Assamese%20heartland.%20It%20is%20also%20in%20Upper%20Assam%20that%20the%20efficacy%20of%20ULFA%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98sentinel%E2%80%99%20of%20Assamese%20interests%20has%20not%20died%20down%20fully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20Rajkhowa%20faction%20have%20publicly%20stated%20that%20they%20have%20no%20political%20ambitions%2C%20what%20stops%20them%20from%20publicly%20endorsing%20the%20party%20that%20delivered%20the%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20crucial%202024%20elections%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20can%20project%20the%20Assamese%20public%20that%20they%20brought%20home%20an%20%E2%80%98honourable%E2%80%99%20agreement%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20that%20with%20the%20entire%20South%20India%20now%20virtually%20BJP-mukt%2C%20the%20party%20desperately%20needs%20to%20shore%20up%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20possible%20from%20other%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%20If%20reviving%20the%20frenzy%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20in%20West%20Bengal%20before%20the%202024%20polls%20can%20help%20dress%20up%20BJP%20as%20always%20working%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20a%20large%20swathe%20of%20Bengalis%2C%20in%20Assam%20too%2C%20an%20accord%20with%20the%20pro-talks%20faction%20of%20ULFA%20should%20be%20able%20to%20project%20to%20the%20majority%20Assamese%20community%20that%20the%20party%20is%20indeed%20pro-%3Cem%3EKhilonjia%3C%2Fem%3E%20(indigenous).%20The%20BJP%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20another%20direct%20beneficiary%20of%20this%20timely%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20the%20third%20direct%20beneficiary.%20Time%20and%20again%2C%20he%20has%20to%20prove%20his%20worth%20to%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20his%20new%20party%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20hot%20seat.%20The%20chief%20minister%20can%20do%20that%20only%20by%20delivering%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20126%20seats%20of%20Assam%20during%20an%20assembly%20election%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2014%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20during%20a%20parliamentary%20poll.%20In%20the%202024%20campaign%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20his%20voice%20about%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20having%20arrived%20in%20Assam%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Northeast%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98Modi%20sarkar%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20loudest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20must%20the%20common%20Assamese%20do%20to%20ensure%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreements%20never%20take%20place%20in%20their%20name%3B%20their%20%3Cem%3Ekhilonjia%3C%2Fem%3E%20sentiments%20can%20never%20be%20misused%20by%20one%20political%20group%20or%20the%20other%20in%20future%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20is%20already%20lit%20if%20lessons%20from%20history%20are%20learnt.%20The%20answer%20clearly%20is%20not%20in%20taking%20up%20guns.%20Let%20history%20be%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20guns%20have%20only%20brought%20bodies%20home%2C%20often%20to%20the%20poorest%20families.%20The%20gun%20culture%20in%20Assam%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Northeast%20has%20only%20helped%20produce%20a%20set%20of%20self-serving%20political%20leaders%20by%20misusing%20community%20sentiments%3B%20have%20served%20only%20some%20political%20parties%E2%80%99%20desperation%20to%20win%20an%20election%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protracted%20ULFA%20movement%20generated%20a%20bunch%20of%20Assamese%20youth%20to%20go%20for%20easy%20money%20through%20extortions%20and%20helped%20create%20a%20batch%20of%20selfish%20Assamese%20businessmen%20who%20have%20little%20interest%20in%20building%20any%20public%20good%20apart%20but%20only%20to%20fill%20their%20personal%20%3Cem%3Ebhoral%20%3C%2Fem%3E(coffer).%20This%20should%2C%20by%20now%2C%20be%20an%20eye%20opener%20for%20the%20community%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Assamese%20youth%20and%20society%20in%20general%20must%20then%20focus%20on%2C%20and%20stridently%20so%2C%20is%20to%20gun%20only%20for%20self-reliance.%20Till%20the%20land%20you%20own%3B%20there%20is%20no%20shame%20in%20it.%20It%20can%20not%20only%20make%20you%20self-sufficient%20but%20also%20help%20generate%20employment%20in%20rural%20areas.%20It%20may%20help%20turn%20the%20trend%20of%20Assamese%20villages%20increasingly%20becoming%20the%20cesspool%20of%20cheap%20labour%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20and%20more%20youth%20must%20start%20believing%20in%20their%20business%20acumen%3B%20allow%20their%20competitive%20nature%20to%20flower.%20They%20must%20strive%20to%20know%20their%20history%2C%20not%20tailored%20by%20any%20political%20force%20to%20push%20their%20agenda%20but%20those%20by%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20greats%3B%20they%20have%20left%20enough%20material%20for%20the%20generations%20to%20know%20who%20is%20truly%20an%20Assamese.%20The%20strive%20for%20%E2%80%98independence%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20community%2C%20and%20the%20state%20in%20turn%2C%20must%20be%20in%20ensuring%20that%20individual%20hard%20work%20contributes%20to%20creating%20a%20collective%20good.%20This%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20must%20prod%20us%20towards%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20several%20success%20stories%20of%20entrepreneurship%20already%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20silent%20revolution%20of%20sorts%20has%20begun.%20The%20focus%20must%20be%20to%20add%20to%20it%20a%20swarm%20of%20more%20such%20stories.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20a%20community%20can%20have%20political%20heft%20only%20when%20it%20has%20economic%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20aim%20for%20the%20community%20must%20be%20to%20embrace%20excellence.%20An%20important%20component%20of%20it%20is%2C%20but%2C%20to%20produce%20leaders%20with%20integrity%20and%20spine%2C%20in%20every%20field.%20It%20also%20means%20discarding%20those%20who%20are%20purely%20self-serving%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20political%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clutch%20of%20resolve%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20delivering%20greater%20profit%20to%20the%20Assamese%20public%20in%20general%20than%20banking%20on%20an%20elusive%20saviour%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%E2%80%99%20agreement%20with%20tall%20promises%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20realise%20later%20that%20it%20was%20not%20quite%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703944990000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30190015%2FEffect-48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-historic-peace-accord-with-ulfa-lost-its-worth-even-before-it-was-inked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20agreement%20is%20just%20another%20addition%20to%20a%20litany%20of%20previous%20'historic'%20agreements%20signed%20with%20militant%20groups%20in%20the%20region.%20Only%20time%20will%20tell%20whether%20this%20'historic'%20accord%20stands%20out%20from%20others%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20hollow.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-historic-peace-accord-with-ulfa-lost-its-worth-even-before-it-was-inked%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLost%2016%20In%20A%20Row%26quot%3B%3A%20Iceland%20Cricket's%20Jibe%20At%20Pakistan%2C%20Hafeez%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIceland%20Cricket%20has%20taken%20a%20jibe%20at%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Hafeez%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F557-mohammad-hafeez-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Hafeez%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20director%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Binconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20technology%20curse%26quot%3B%20cost%20them%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20against%20Australia%20at%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20made%20some%20mistakes%20as%20a%20team%2C%20we%20will%20take%20that%2C%20we%20will%20address%20those%20things%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20I%20believe%20inconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20technology%20curse%20(has)%20really%20given%20us%20the%20result%20which%20should%20have%20been%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hafeez%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Hafeez's%20comments%2C%20Iceland%20Cricket%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20amazing.%20How%20can%20the%20more%20talented%20and%20superior%20team%20have%20lost%2016%20matches%20in%20a%20row%20in%20Australia%3F%20Surely%20those%20lucky%20Aussies%20will%20stop%20being%20lucky%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt's%20amazing.%20How%20can%20the%20more%20talented%20and%20superior%20team%20have%20lost%2016%20matches%20in%20a%20row%20in%20Australia%3F%20Surely%20those%20lucky%20Aussies%20will%20stop%20being%20lucky%20soon.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F118gmMCe2K%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F118gmMCe2K%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Iceland%20Cricket%20(%40icelandcricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ficelandcricket%2Fstatus%2F1740869871976808528%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20needed%2098%20runs%20with%205%20wickets%20in%20hand%20in%20the%20chase%20of%20317%20when%20Mohammad