t%20of%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20director%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703944560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F8lgolte8_mohammad-hafeez-x_625x300_30_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flost-16-matches-in-a-row-iceland-crickets-jibe-at-pakistan-mohammad-hafeez-goes-viral-4770587%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iceland%20Cricket%20has%20taken%20a%20jibe%20at%20Mohammad%20Hafeez%20after%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20director%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Binconsistent%20umpiring%20and%20technology%20curse%26quot%3B%20cost%20them%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20against%20Australia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flost-16-matches-in-a-row-iceland-crickets-jibe-at-pakistan-mohammad-hafeez-goes-viral-4770587%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flost-16-matches-in-a-row-iceland-crickets-jibe-at-pakistan-mohammad-hafeez-goes-viral-4770587%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Flost-16-matches-in-a-row-iceland-crickets-jibe-at-pakistan-mohammad-hafeez-goes-viral-4770587%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reflections%20on%20a%20Disturbing%20Year%20Gone%20By.%20And%20the%20Challenges%20That%20Lie%20Ahead.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20ends%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20doom.%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20Palestine.%20It%20is%20about%20our%20own%20country%2C%20India.%20The%20images%20of%20a%20heavily-garlanded%20Brijbhushan%20Singh%20with%20a%20victory%20sign%20celebrating%20the%20win%20of%20his%20proxy%20in%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20post%20of%20president%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20juxtaposed%20with%20the%20image%20of%20the%20decorated%20Olympian%20wrestler%20Sakshi%20Malik%20crying%20and%20hanging%20up%20her%20shoes%20before%20the%20media%20define%20the%20state%20and%20mood%20of%20India%20in%20our%20times.%20Malik%2C%20along%20with%20some%20other%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20had%20levelled%20charges%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20molestation%20against%20Singh%20and%20had%20been%20fighting%20against%20him%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Singh%2C%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%2C%20clearly%20has%20the%20full%20support%20of%20his%20party%20and%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20a%20sad%20reflection%20on%20us%20all%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20thinks%20there%20will%20be%20no%20political%20price%20to%20pay%20if%20it%20ignores%20the%20cries%20of%20these%20women%20athletes%20who%20have%20risen%20from%20the%20dusty%20lanes%20of%20villages%20and%20done%20the%20country%20proud%20by%20winning%20in%20international%20competitions.%20The%20country%20saw%20a%20stormy%20agitation%20after%20a%20woman%20was%20raped%20in%20Delhi%20only%2011%20years%20back.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20mass%20movement%20of%20sympathy%20or%20solidarity%20for%20them.%20Our%20campuses%20remained%20calm%20even%20when%20the%20images%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20being%20dragged%20away%20from%20their%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20went%20viral.%20It%20did%20not%20cause%20a%20ripple%20in%20the%20consciousness%20of%20the%20people%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20treated%20them%20with%20contempt%2C%20smelled%20conspiracy%20in%20their%20charges%20and%20agitation%2C%20and%20mocked%20them.%20The%20Delhi%20police%2C%20which%20had%20arrested%20the%20fact-checker%20journalist%20Md%20Zubair%20on%20laughably%20flimsy%20charges%20under%20POCSO%2C%20dragged%20its%20feet%2C%20and%20even%20after%20concluding%20that%20Singh%20did%20commit%20sexual%20offences%2C%20not%20once%20but%20multiple%20times%2C%20decided%20to%20let%20him%20remain%20free.%20There%20was%20no%20media%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20days%20we%20also%20saw%20the%20mass%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20belonging%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%20from%20both%20houses.%20Yet%2C%20the%20news%20of%20crucial%20bills%20being%20passed%20in%20the%20near%20total%20absence%20of%20the%20opposition%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20disturbed%20the%20media%20and%2C%20through%20them%2C%20the%20wider%20public.%20Everything%20is%20being%20done%20with%20the%20force%20of%20numbers.%20Where%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20complaint%3F%20The%20opposition%20MPs%20are%20asked%20to%20behave%20and%20respect%20the%20majority.%20The%20media%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20warning%20the%20people%20of%20the%20serious%20consequences%20these%20new%20laws%20are%20going%20to%20have%20on%20all%20aspects%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20has%20mildly%20complained%20about%20the%20breach%20of%20parliamentary%20processes%20but%20has%20got%20busy%20with%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20supposedly%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20discussing%20the%20list%20of%20invitees%20and%20who%20is%20being%20honoured%20with%20the%20invitation%20and%20who%20has%20been%20left%20out.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20your%20reputation%20depends%20on%20your%20place%20in%20the%20invitee%20list.%20We%20have%20heard%20about%20some%20prominent%20opposition%20members%20being%20invited.%20But%20we%20do%20not%20expect%20them%20to%20reject%20the%20invite%20by%20pointing%20to%20the%20criminal%20way%20in%20which%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98legal%E2%80%99%20usurpation%20of%20its%20land%20for%20the%20temple%2C%20and%20why%20it%20is%20unholy%20to%20build%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%20of%20what%20the%20Supreme%20court%20called%20an%20%E2%80%98egregious%20crime%E2%80%99%20committed%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20upholding%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20refusing%20to%20rule%20on%20the%20legality%20of%20turning%20the%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20once%20again%20shown%20its%20willingness%20to%20legally%20legitimize%20acts%20of%20majoritarianism.%20It%20has%2C%20by%20doing%20this%2C%20pursued%20its%20logic%20of%20%E2%80%98what%20is%20done%20is%20done%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98what%20the%20government%20wills%2C%20will%20happen.%E2%80%99%20This%20is%20in%20keeping%20with%20its%202019%20Babri%20Mosque%20judgment%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20land%20to%20those%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%202023%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20ruling%20allowing%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98archaeological%20survey%E2%80%99%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20changing%20the%20character%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20making%20the%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20redundant.%20The%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20designed%20to%20keep%20the%20nation%20together%2C%20is%20being%20systematically%20dismantled%2C%20and%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20facilitating%20it%2C%20even%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20keeps%20giving%20weekend%20speeches%20waxing%20eloquent%20about%20great%20constitutional%20and%20humanist%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20judiciary%20led%20by%20the%20incumbent%20CJI%2C%20like%20his%20predecessors%2C%20is%20breathtaking.%20While%20speaking%20for%20individual%20liberty%20endlessly%2C%20the%20CJI%2C%20as%20master%20of%20the%20roster%2C%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20bail%20petitions%20of%20people%20arrested%20(clearly%20because%20of%20their%20politics)%20end%20up%20before%20judges%20known%20for%20their%20aversion%20to%20the%20primacy%20of%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20judiciary%20refusing%20to%20perform%20its%20role%20as%20constitutional%20watchdog%2C%20it%20seems%20impossible%20to%20stop%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Efrom%20reconfiguring%20the%20constitutional%20frame.%20The%20party%20has%20numbers%20and%20is%20getting%20no%20pushback%20from%20the%20elites%20of%20India.%20The%20corporate%20world%20adopted%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20its%20man%20way%20back%20in%202007%20%E2%80%93%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ein%20return%20for%20which%20he%20has%20allowed%20the%2C%20to%20capture%20all%20the%20national%20and%20natural%20resources%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20endless%20violence%20and%20hateful%20propaganda%2C%20society%20has%20been%20torn%20apart%20so%20badly%20that%20the%20Indian%20nation%20as%20a%20shared%20zone%20of%20sensibilities%20is%20coming%20under%20severe%20strain.%20One%20can%20see%20this%20starkly%20in%20Manipur.%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20violence%20with%20state%20patronage%20has%20wrecked%20the%20state%20and%20divided%20it%20into%20two%20parts%20which%20now%20cannot%20sit%20face%20to%20face.%20Kukis%20have%20lost%20all%20hope%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20valley%2C%20and%20Meiteis%20cannot%20go%20to%20the%20hills.%20Kukis%20have%20managed%20to%20safeguard%20themselves%20as%20they%20have%20hills%20to%20fortify%20themselves%20in%20and%20also%20resources%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20violence%20they%20have%20faced.%20But%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20other%20minorities%20do%20not%20have%20this%20%E2%80%98advantage%E2%80%99%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20minorities%20or%20any%20socially%20vulnerable%20section%20of%20the%20population%20cannot%20expect%20protection%20from%20the%20state%20apparatus%2C%20including%20the%20judiciary.%20Civil%20society%20has%20been%20effectively%20disabled.%20The%20media%20has%20done%20its%20best%20to%20convince%20the%20people%20that%20members%20of%20civil%20society%20are%20their%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20ebbs%20with%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%20Khalid%20Saifi%20and%20Gulfisha%20Fatima%20completing%20three%20years%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20jails%20and%20Shoma%20Sen%2C%20Mahesh%20Raut%2C%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20and%20others%20completing%20five%20years%20in%20the%20jails%20of%20Maharashtra.%20They%20are%20forgotten%20people%20who%20fought%20for%20lost%20causes.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20media%E2%80%99s%20indifference%20to%20their%20plight%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20do%20not%20relate%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20now%20to%20analyse%20and%20our%20job%20is%20merely%20to%20record%20and%20describe%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Indian%20dream.%20But%20this%20is%20luxury%20people%20in%20India%20cannot%20afford.%20Sitting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20a%20gloomy%20winter%20day%20I%20feel%20helpless.%20But%20then%20I%20get%20calls%20from%20a%20farmer%20friend%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20is%20a%20Muslim.%20From%20a%20state%20which%20is%20most%20oppressive%20for%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20practise%20democracy.%20For%20Muslims%20even%20more%20so.%20Here%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20who%20believes%20that%202024%20is%20still%20open.%20We%20can%20still%20turn%20the%20tide%20and%20recover%20our%20democracy.%20He%20has%20a%20plan%20and%20also%20friends%20and%20he%20wants%20political%20parties%20to%20listen%20to%20him.%20Or%20my%20friends%20from%20a%20youth%20group%20in%20Pune%20who%20have%20been%20training%20workers%20of%20different%20political%20parties%20and%20reminding%20them%20that%20the%20fight%20is%20for%20larger%20ideas%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20gains%20that%20power%20brings.%20And%20they%20feel%20encouraged%20that%20party%20workers%20listen.%20And%20then%20our%20friend%20Alok%20Shukla%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20informs%20us%20that%20the%20adivasis%20of%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%20are%20still%20fighting%20against%20mining%20and%20their%20dispossession%2C%20even%20after%20knowing%20that%20the%20state%20has%20a%20more%20brutal%20government%20in%20power%20now.%20The%20parents%20and%20partners%20of%20those%20in%20prison%20still%20keep%20reminding%20the%20courts%20of%20their%20duty.%20I%20see%20the%20images%20of%20calm%20Muslim%20women%20carrying%20Palestinian%20flags%20which%20are%20snatched%20by%20the%20policemen%20and%20torn.%20She%20looks%20at%20him%20disapprovingly%20but%20keeps%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20sign%20off%2C%20my%20doorbell%20rings.%20Here%20is%20my%20young%20journalist%20friend%20from%20Punjab.%20He%20is%20on%20way%20to%20Chandigarh%20after%20spending%20the%20week%20with%20the%20wrestlers%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20Bajrang%20Punia%20and%20others.%20He%20is%20upbeat.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20you%20think%20it%20is%20a%20victory%20that%20these%20wrestlers%20who%20could%20not%20think%20beyond%20awards%20only%20a%20year%20back%20now%20stand%20upright%20before%20a%20mighty%20state%20knowing%20well%20what%20they%20are%20up%20against%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asks.%20%C2%A0%20I%20cannot%20but%20agree.%20The%20fight%20is%20still%20left%20in%20us.%20It%20is%20not%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703944225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27210340%2FEffect.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freflections-on-a-disturbing-year-gone-by-and-the-challenges-that-lie-ahead%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20endless%20violence%20and%20hateful%20propaganda%2C%20the%20Indian%20nation%20as%20a%20shared%20zone%20of%20sensibilities%20is%20coming%20under%20severe%20strain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Freflections-on-a-disturbing-year-gone-by-and-the-challenges-that-lie-ahead%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunny%20says%20he%20walked%20out%20during%20this%20scene%20in%20Animal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703943784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106406059%2Cimgsize-57402.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollyw