as%20much%20as%20a%20salaam.%20I%20put%20two%20and%20two%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20said%20heartily.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20feel%20bad.%20I%20myself%20eat%20at%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20bear%20this%20swine%E2%80%99s%20qorma%20any%20longer.%20But%20Rahman%20miyan%20is%20becoming%20too%20expensive%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20Unaffordable!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20old%20Rahmania%20hotel%20was%20now%20formally%20called%20Al-haaj%20Al-Rahman%20hotel.%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20its%20owner%2C%20had%20gone%20to%20haj%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20and%2C%20upon%20his%20return%2C%20changed%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Rahmania%20hotel%20to%20Haji%20Abdul%20Rahman%20hotel%20and%20then%2C%20finally%2C%20to%20Al-haaj%20Al-Rahman%20hotel.%20People%20sometimes%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20haji%20saheb%2C%20in%20deference%20to%20his%20having%20performed%20haj%2C%20but%20nobody%20in%20the%20old%20city%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20change%20in%20the%20restaurant%E2%80%99s%20name.%20There%20was%20a%20freshly%20painted%20signboard%20that%20had%20the%20new%20name%20printed%20in%20black%20across%20a%20white%20background.%20A%20picture%20of%20the%20Ka%E2%80%99aba%20and%20the%20Mosque%20in%20Madina%20adorned%20the%20top%20left%20corner%2C%20while%20two%20chubby%20toddlers%20with%20rather%20red%20lips%2C%20attired%20in%20white%20kurtas%20and%20black%20topis%2C%20embraced%20each%20other%20in%20the%20right%20hand%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20found%20Habib%20waiting%20at%20a%20safe%20distance%20from%20the%20hotel.%20He%20often%20carried%20a%20bulky%20knapsack%20with%20him%20and%20stood%20slightly%20bent%20under%20its%20weight.%20His%20pimply%20face%20with%20its%20scraggly%20beard%20lit%20up%20in%20recognition%20as%20he%20saw%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20standing%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20scared%20to%20go%20in%20alone.%20Everyone%20says%20to%20be%20careful%20of%20haji%20saheb.%20He%20is%20always%20trying%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20the%20sly%20and%20inform%20on%20the%20community.%20Plus%20he%20has%20also%20become%20a%20bore%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20He%20catches%20people%20and%20starts%20to%20sermonise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20rolled%20his%20eyes.%20%E2%80%9CAchcha%3F%20Let%E2%80%99s%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20and%20strutted%20inside.%20He%20stood%20in%20the%20centre%2C%20winked%20at%20Habib%20and%20then%2C%20grinning%2C%20caught%20hold%20of%20Arshad%2C%20the%20chief%20waiter%2C%20%E2%80%9CArre%20Arshad%2C%20get%20us%20a%20plate%20of%20falafel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20smiled%20too%2C%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20apparent%20punch%20line%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20a%20falafel%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20started%20to%20giggle%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20have%20you%20kept%20an%20Arabi%20name%20for%20your%20hotel%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20Arabi%20food%3F%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20looked%20bemused%2C%20but%20he%20laughed%20along%20gamely.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20Arabi%20name%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20craned%20his%20neck%20to%20look%20at%20the%20signboard%20outside%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20was%20in%20English.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20miyan%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20elderly%20Rahman%20called%20out%20to%20him%20from%20behind%20his%20counter.%20He%20sat%20on%20a%20wooden%20chair%2C%20with%20an%20old%20wooden%20cupboard%20behind%20him.%20He%20locked%20his%20money%20and%20his%20account%20books%20in%20it%2C%20and%20also%20his%20black%20sherwani%2C%20which%20he%20wore%20when%20he%20went%20out.%20On%20his%20table%20were%20a%20steel%20flask%20with%20his%20filtered%20water%2C%20and%20a%20small%20coal%20iron%20with%20which%20Arshad%20would%20smoothen%20out%20the%20creases%20on%20his%20sherwani.%20Haji%20Abdul%20Rahman%20was%20a%20vain%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20had%20a%20stentorian%20voice.%20%E2%80%9CArshad%20didn%E2%80%99t%20name%20the%20restaurant.%20You%20should%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20these%20matters.%20I%20decided%20to%20change%20the%20name%20to%20make%20it%20more%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20culture.%E2%80%9D%20Abdul%20Rahman%20looked%20pompously%20around%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20with%20the%20grace%20of%20God%2C%20my%20business%20is%20doing%20very%20well.%20Even%20foreigners%20come%20to%20eat%20here.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20hoarding%20wealth.%20That%20is%20not%20allowed%20in%20our%20religion.%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20work%20for%20the%20community.%20Ten%20years%20ago%20I%20started%20the%20madarsa%20and%20to%20this%20day%20I%20am%20continuing%20to%20provide%20for%20the%20madarsa%20boys%20%E2%80%93%20boarding%2C%20lodging%2C%20everything.%20I%20am%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20get%20an%20Islamic%20upbringing.%20Alhamdulillah%2C%20we%20have%20saved%20so%20many%20of%20them%20from%20a%20life%20of%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20surely%20guaranteed%20a%20place%20in%20paradise%2C%20haji%20saheb.%20Some%20say%20you%E2%80%99ve%20saved%20boys%20from%20lives%20of%20crime%20by%20snitching%20on%20them%20and%20sending%20them%20to%20jail%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20so%20that%20they%20never%20think%20of%20irritating%20the%20authorities%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%20Abdul%20Rahman%20narrowed%20his%20eyes%20and%20nodded.%20He%20pulled%20a%20plastic%20chair%20towards%20his%20own%20wooden%20one%20and%20gestured%20for%20Jamal%20to%20sit%20down.%20%E2%80%9CCome%2C%20come%20sit%20Jamal%20miyan.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20to%20talk.%20You%20hardly%20come%20here%20anymore.%20People%20who%20are%20jealous%20of%20my%20success%20have%20spread%20these%20rumours%20about%20me.%20I%20look%20after%20community%20boys%20%E2%80%93%20they%20all%20come%20to%20me%20for%20help.%20I%20have%20helped%20clear%20encroachments%20on%20waqf%20properties.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20authorities%20and%20had%20extra%20forces%20posted%20in%20the%20area%20to%20ensure%20peace%20during%20tense%20times.%20I%20have%20met%20the%20local%20MLA%20on%20many%20occasions%20to%20inform%20him%20of%20our%20problems.%20I%20do%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20community%2C%20but%20I%20do%20it%20quietly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaji%20saheb%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20true%20community%20leader.%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20stand%20for%20elections%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20giving%20tickets%20to%20Muslim%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20sighed.%20Habib%20had%20inched%20closer%20too.%20He%20said%20softly%2C%20%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20we%20eat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHabib%20miyan%2C%20what%20have%20you%20been%20protesting%20about%20these%20days%3F%20Gaza%20is%20over%20now%3F%20Have%20you%20found%20some%20other%20issue%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGaza%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over%2C%20haji%20saheb.%20And%20new%20issues%20keep%20coming%20up%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Quran%20says%20that%20everything%20is%20the%20will%20of%20Allah.%20So%20what%20is%20there%20to%20mourn%20and%20to%20protest%2C%20hain%3F%20See%20I%20run%20a%20business%3B%20I%20also%20run%20a%20madarsa%20%E2%80%93%20one%20has%20to%20learn%20to%20adjust.%20Bend%20a%20little%2C%20ignore%20some%20things.%20Cannot%20always%20be%20demanding%20rights%2C%20hain%3F%20See%2C%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20trouble%20others%2C%20nobody%20will%20trouble%20you.%20I%20donated%20for%20the%20temple%20also.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20a%20good%20Muslim%2C%20haji%20saheb.%20Laadley%20has%20grown%20a%20full%20henna%20coloured%20beard%20under%20your%20influence%2C%20but%20he%20isn%E2%80%99t%20such%20a%20good%20Muslim%20as%20you.%20He%20stands%20up%20for%20himself%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal%20as%20he%20rose%20from%20the%20chair.%20%E2%80%9CHabibi%20is%20treating%20me%20to%20paaya.%20We%20will%20go%20order%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20face%20darkened.%20%E2%80%9CJamal%20saheb%2C%20some%20times%20you%20stand%20up%20for%20yourself%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20by%20being%20less%20strident.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20brag%2C%20but%20what%20is%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20standing%2C%20other%20than%20providing%20an%20adda%20for%20local%20wastrels%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20got%20up%20purposefully%20from%20his%20chair%20and%20pointed%20to%20an%20empty%20table%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlease!%20When%20the%20Day%20of%20Judgment%20comes%2C%20let%20yourselves%20be%20found%20chewing%20on%20a%20boti.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boys%20grinned%20at%20each%20other%20as%20they%20slid%20on%20to%20the%20bench%20at%20the%20table.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20we%20upset%20him%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20he%20upset%20me%20even%20more.%20This%20whole%20place%20is%20becoming%20unbearable%20I%20tell%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20plates%20of%20paaya%2C%20Arshad!%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20called%20out%20to%20the%20waiter.%20%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20I%20think%20you%20are%20becoming%20angry%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20this%20novel%3F%20The%20jasoosi%20novel%2C%20murder%20mystery%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20have%20written%20out%20the%20characters.%20Now%20I%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20will%20die.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKill%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20said%20nodding%20at%20Rahman%20miyan.%20%E2%80%98He%20is%20becoming%20very%20irritating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20flippant%2C%20Jamal%20bhai.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20proper%20story.%20But%20if%20I%20had%20to%20kill%20someone%20in%20my%20jasoosi%20novel%2C%20it%E2%80%99d%20be%20that%20scoundrel%20Awdhesh%20Rana.%20He%20slapped%20me%20for%20nothing!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20go%20to%20jail%20for%20even%20thinking%20such%20thoughts.%20Kill%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20idiot%20husband%3B%20nobody%20would%20care.%20And%20make%20Salman%20the%20murderer.%20Again%20nobody%20would%20care.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20brought%20two%20bowls%20with%20oily%20gravy%20spilling%20on%20to%20the%20sides%20and%20put%20them%20on%20the%20table.%20He%20placed%20two%20fat%20aabi%20rotis%20on%20top%20of%20the%20bowls%2C%20and%20sat%20on%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20bench%20next%20to%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20harass%20haji%20saheb%20so%20much%3F%20It%20gives%20leeway%20to%20others%20also.%20He%20is%20such%20a%20pious%20man%3B%20he%20has%20helped%20so%20many%20people.%20He%20has%20literally%20brought%20up%20Abrar%20bhai%20and%20me%20%E2%80%93%20took%20us%20in%20as%20children%2C%20trained%20us%2C%20and%20now%20I%20manage%20everything.%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20Abrar%20was%20the%20cook%20who%20had%20made%20Rahmania%20famous%20for%20its%20paaya%20and%20kababs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20after%20the%20restaurant%20closes%2C%20he%20first%20does%20the%20accounts%20and%20then%20he%20prays%20tahajjud%20namaz%20till%20late.%20Eats%20whatever%20is%20left%20and%20only%20after%20he%20finishes%20his%20prayer%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Arshad%20admiringly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20tore%20off%20a%20piece%20of%20his%20roti%20and%20dunked%20it%20in%20the%20shorba%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20come%2C%20the%20pieces%20of%20gosht%20become%20fewer%20and%20fewer.%20Will%20the%20madarsa%20run%20on%20my%20money%20only%3F%20All%20the%20goodwill%20is%20going%20to%20others%2C%20and%20the%20money%20is%20coming%20from%20us%20poor%20people.%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20looked%20very%20embarrassed.%20Arshad%20made%20a%20gesture%20with%20his%20right%20hand%2C%20twirling%20the%20wrist%20with%20fingers%20in%20the%20air%2C%20to%20suggest%20that%20Jamal%20was%20uttering%20absurdities.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20not%20Abrar%20bhai%E2%80%99s%20fault%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20muttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20counter%2C%20Rahman%20miyan%20coughed%20delicately%2C%20but%20loudly%20enough%20to%20indicate%20that%20he%20had%20also%20heard%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20finished%20the%20paaya%2C%20Jamal%20called%20out%20to%20Arshad%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CArshad%20bhai%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20for%20meetha%20today%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20been%20coughing%20fitfully%20in%20the%20background.%20Habib%20turned%20to%20look%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20happened%20to%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20mumbled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20keep%20any%20meetha%2C%20you%20know%20that.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20have%20been%20telling%20haji%20saheb%20that%20we%20should%20make%20kheer%20at%20least%2C%20if%20not%20shahi%20tukda.%20Everyone%20asks%20for%20meetha%20after%20such%20a%20heavy%20meal%2C%20but%20he%20is%20very%20disciplined.%20He%20says%20sugar%20is%20bad%20for%20health.%20He%20has%20high%20sugar%20himself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaji%20saheb%20now%20ambled%20over%20to%20their%20table%2C%20having%20apparently%20forgotten%20the%20earlier%20unpleasantness.%20He%20evidently%20practiced%20what%20he%20preached.%20%E2%80%9CJamal%20miyan%2C%20at%20your%20age%20you%20should%20be%20more%20fit.%20You%20have%20put%20on%20so%20much%20weight.%20Look%20at%20me%3A%20I%20inherited%20sugar%2C%20BP%20and%20cholesterol%20from%20my%20father%2C%20but%20everything%20is%20under%20check.%20I%20am%20very%20careful%20about%20what%20I%20eat.%20Your%20chachi%20sends%20home%20cooked%20food%20in%20a%20big%20tiffin%20carrier.%20Only%20my%20asthma%20is%20killing%20me%20because%20of%20this%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20is%20a%20special%20day%2C%20haji%20saheb.%20Habibi%20has%20started%20to%20write%20his%20jasoosi%20novel.%20Send%20Arshad%20to%20bring%20some%20mithai%20from%20Shambhu%E2%80%99s%20shop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBalance%20is%20very%20important%20in%20life.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20children%20of%20my%20own%3B%20Allah%E2%80%99s%20wish.%20Your%20chachi%20has%20one%20neph