ing%20coach%20Vikram%20Rathour%20asked%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BTu%20is%20net%20pe%20aayega%26quot%3B%20(would%20you%20like%20to%20use%20this%20one)%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20nets%20exclusively%20kept%20for%20throwdowns%2C%20the%20skipper%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BNahi%20yehin%20pe%20aur%2010%20minute%20bat%20karoonga%26quot%3B%20(No%20I%20will%20bat%20here%20for%20another%2010%20minutes).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skipper%20devoted%20extra%20time%20for%20Mukesh%20and%20it%20seemed%20he%20was%20giving%20tips%20on%20wrist%20position%20and%20the%20length%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20hit%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20has%20been%20consistently%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20for%20Bengal%20featuring%20in%20two%20Ranji%20Trophv%20finals%20in%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%2C%20he%20did%20ask%20a%20few%20probing%20questions%20of%20the%20Indian%20captain%20and%20certainly%20made%20a%20case%20for%20himself%20for%20the%20Newlands%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMhambrey%20works%20on%20Prasidh's%20length%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20surprise%20if%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prasidh%20Krishna%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107509-prasidh-krishna-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20his%20forgettable%20debut%2C%20gets%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20in%20the%20next%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%20from%20being%20Test%20match%20ready%2C%20it%20was%20time%20for%20him%20to%20get%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasidh%20didn't%20bowl%20to%20any%20batters%20at%20the%20nets%20as%20the%20lanky%20man%20from%20Bengaluru%20sought%20to%20figure%20out%20what's%20the%20right%20length%20to%20hit%20in%20South%20African%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowling%20coach%20Paras%20Mhambrey%20paid%20singular%20attention%20to%20Prasidh%20during%20the%2075%20odd%20minutes%20that%20he%