said%20the%20strength%20of%20'vikas'%20(development)%20and%20'virasat'%20(heritage)%20would%20take%20India%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20historic%20moment%20of%20the%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20here%20while%20appealing%20to%20people%20to%20not%20come%20on%20the%20day%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20business%20of%20people%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world%20coming%20to%20Ayodhya%20had%20started%20and%20would%20go%20on%20till%20eternity%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20also%20appealed%20for%20a%20resolve%20to%20make%20town%20the%20cleanest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20meeting%20after%20inaugurating%20the%20Maharshi%20Valmiki%20airport%20and%20the%20redeveloped%20station%20named%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20from%20where%20he%20flagged%20off%20two%20Amrit%20Bharat%20and%20six%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%2C%20some%20virtually%2C%20he%20appealed%20to%20all%20citizens%20to%20light%20diyas%20in%20their%20houses%20on%20January%2022%20so%20the%20whole%20country%20basks%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarking%20January%2022%20as%20a%20special%20day%2C%20he%20also%20asked%20people%20to%20launch%20cleanliness%20drives%20at%20pilgrimage%20sites%20and%20temples%20across%20the%20country%20from%20Makar%20Sankranti%20on%20January%2014%20till%20the%20temple%20consecration%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20%26quot%3Bliving%20under%20a%20tent%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20now%20he%20will%20get%20a%20concrete%20house%20like%20the%20four%20crore%20poor%20who%20got%20pucca%20houses%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ujjwala%20scheme%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20transformed%20the%20lives%20of%20crores%20of%20mothers%20and%20sisters.%20Only%2014%20crore%20gas%20connections%20were%20given%20in%20five%20decades%2C%20but%20his%20government%20in%20a%20decade%20gave%2018%20crore%2C%20including%2010%20crore%20free%20of%20cost%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20he%20stopped%20by%20at%20the%20home%20of%20an%20Ujjwala%20beneficiary%20Meera%20Majhi.%20He%20met%20the%20family%20in%20her%20humble%20home%20and%20was%20also%20seen%20drinking%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20inaugurated%2C%20dedicated%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2015%2C700%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20comprise%20projects%20worth%20about%20Rs%2011%2C100%20crore%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20city%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20and%20those%20worth%20about%20Rs%204%2C600%20crore%20related%20to%20other%20works%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20in%201992%20catapulted%20to%20global%20headlines%20with%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Babri%20Masjid%20by%20a%20group%20of%20kar%20sevaks%20who%20believed%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20was%20one%20of%20dances%2C%20music%20and%20the%20many%20folk%20colours%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20states.%20After%20he%20arrived%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20PM%20Modi%20held%20a%20roadshow%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20and%20was%20greeted%20by%20hundreds%20of%20people%20lining%20alongside%20the%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20greeted%20people%20from%20his%20car%20and%20at%20one%20point%20opened%20the%20door%20of%20his%20vehicle%20to%20wave%20back%20at%20them.%20People%20showered%20flower%20petals%2C%20waved%20BJP%20flags%20and%20raised%20slogans%20in%20his%20praise.%20The%20prime%20minister%20also%20witnessed%20performances%20by%20cultural%20troupes%20along%20the%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20office%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20more%20than%201%2C400%20performers%20would%20present%20folk%20art%20and%20cultural%20programmes%20on%2040%20stages%20along%20the%20route%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20group%20of%20women%20from%20Rajasthan%20danced%20the%20'Chakri'%20to%20lilting%20tunes%2C%20another%20from%20Prayagraj%20performed%20the%20ancient%20folk%20dance%20'Dedhiya'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20believed%20that%20women%20of%20Prayagraj%20danced%20the%20'Dedhiya'%20when%20Ramji%20and%20others%20had%20returned%20from%20Lanka%20after%20Lanka%20Dahan.%20Now%2C%20Ram%20Lalla%20is%20also%20getting%20a%20new%20temple%2C%20so%20the%20divine%20feeling%20have%20come%20back%2C%20so%20this%20performance.%20As%20also%20to%20welcome%20the%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20lead%20dancer%20Preeti%20Singh%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20airport%20and%20railway%20station%20took%20place%20after%20the%20roadshow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20inaugurating%20the%20station%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20took%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20facility.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Adityanath%2C%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20and%20others.%20PM%20Modi%20was%20briefed%20by%20Vaishnaw%20about%20the%20station%2C%20the%20facade%20of%20which%20is%20inspired%20by%20traditional%20temple%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Phase-I%20of%20the%20redeveloped%20station%20--%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20Junction%20Railway%20Station%20--%20has%20been%20completed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%20240%20crore%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-storey%20railway%20station%20building%20is%20equipped%20with%20features%20such%20as%20lifts%2C%20escalators%2C%20food%20plazas%2C%20shops%20for%20puja%20needs%2C%20cloak%20rooms%2C%20child%20care%20rooms%20and%20waiting%20halls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20station%20building%20is%20%26quot%3Baccessible%20for%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3BIGBC%20certified%20green%20station%20building%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20officials%20The%20prime%20minister%20visited%20the%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20Chowk%2C%20where%20a%20giant-size%20veena%20has%20been%20installed.%20In%20keeping%20with%20the%20place%20and%20the%20mood%2C%20a%20bhajan%20by%20the%20late%20music%20queen%20played%20in%20the%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20airport%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Civil%20Aviation%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Civil%20Aviation%20Gen%20(Retired)%20VK%20Singh%20and%20Adityanath%20were%20among%20those%20who%20accompanied%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facade%20of%20the%20terminal%20building%20depicts%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Ram%20temple%20here%2C%20while%20its%20interiors%20are%20decorated%20with%20paintings%20and%20murals%20depicting%20the%20life%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhase-1%20of%20the%20airport%20has%20been%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C450%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%20The%20airport's%20terminal%20building%20will%20have%20an%20area%20of%206%2C500%20sqm%2C%20equipped%20to%20serve%20about%2010%20lakh%20passengers%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20will%20improve%20connectivity%20in%20the%20region%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20boost%20in%20tourism%2C%20business%20activities%20and%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703939280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fm969pof8_pm-modi-in-ayodhya_625x300_30_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhole-world-waiting-for-historic-moment-pm-narendra-modi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-event-4770042%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20a%20festooned%2C%20festive%20Ayodhya%20on%20Saturday%20to%20unveil%20a%20'new%20look%20old'%20city%20with%20an%20airport%2C%20a%20revamped%20train%20station%20and%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2015%2C700%20crore%20ahead%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20next%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhole-world-waiting-for-historic-moment-pm-narendra-modi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-event-4770042%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhole-world-waiting-for-historic-moment-pm-narendra-modi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-event-4770042%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhole-world-waiting-for-historic-moment-pm-narendra-modi-on-ayodhya-ram-temple-event-4770042%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20Must%20Recognise%20VVPAT%20Paper%20Trail%20is%20Central%20to%20Infusing%20Trust%20in%20EVMs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FVVPAT-machine-PIB.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20joint%20protest%20of%20the%2028-party%20Opposition%20Alliance%20INDIA%2C%20on%20December%2022%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20called%20for%20unity%2C%20saying%20democracy%20is%20under%20threat%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20leaders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Funite-to-save-democracy-says-mallikarjun-kharge-at-india-bloc-s-protest-101703238843871.html%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20opposition%20parties%20came%20together%20to%20form%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20because%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Shah%20are%20trying%20to%20destroy%20democracy%20and%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20meeting%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20earlier%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20resolved%20to%20fight%20authoritarianism%20with%20full%20might%20saying%20that%20democracy%20and%20constitution%20are%20under%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20meeting%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20adopted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Findia-bloc-passes-resolution-on-suspension-of-mps-evms-operation-2478038-2023-12-19%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%3A%20%E2%80%9CINDIA%20parties%20reiterate%20that%20there%20are%20many%20doubts%20on%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVMs.%20These%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20many%20experts%20and%20professionals%20as%20well.%20There%20is%20widespread%20demand%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20ballot%20paper%20system%E2%80%A6%20INDIA%20parties%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98happy%E2%80%99%20if%20there%20was%20a%20return%20to%20voting%20through%20ballot%20paper%E2%80%A6%20If%20ECI%20has%20any%20reservations%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20and%20desirable%20to%20have%20a%20hybrid%20ballot%20paper-EVM%20system%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%E2%80%A6%20It%20suggested%20that%20instead%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20falling%20in%20the%20box%2C%20it%20should%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter%20who%20shall%20then%20place%20it%20in%20a%20separate%20ballot%20box%20after%20having%20verified%20his%20or%20her%20choice.%20100%25%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20then%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20solace%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbetter%20late%20than%20never!%E2%80%9D%20But%2C%20with%20parliament%20election%20only%20weeks%20away%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20follow-up%20action%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resolution%20is%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fecisveep-eci-must-implement-its-constitutional-mandate-to-conduct-free-and-fair-election%5C%22%3Eadoption%20of%20the%20public%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20initiated%20by%20civil%20society%20on%20August%2024%2C%20signed%20by%20over%207%2C000%20voters%20and%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ECI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEVM%2FVVPAT%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20essential%20%E2%80%98Democracy%20Principles%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20that%20each%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20is%20cast-as-intended%2C%20recorded-as-cast%20and%20counted-as-recorded.%20Though%20the%20ECI%20has%20arranged%20for%20all%20EVMs%20to%20be%20accompanied%20with%20VVPAT-device%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Voter-Verifiable%20Paper%20Trail%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20the%20level%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98bioscope%E2%80%99%20which%20shows%20up%20a%20tiny%20%E2%80%98paper%20slip%E2%80%99%20for%20seven%20seconds%20which%20then%20vanishes%20and%20is%20NOT%20counted%E2%80%A6.%20The%20VVPAT%20system%20should%20therefore%20be%20re-calibrated%20to%20be%20fully%20voter-verifiable.%20A%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20in%20her%20hand%20and%20cast%20it%20in%20a%20chip-free%20ballot%20box%20for%20the%20vote%20to%20be%20valid.%20These%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20fully%20counted%20for%20all%20constituencies%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20For%20this%20purpose%2C%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20larger%20in%20size%20and%20must%20be%20printed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20can%20be%20preserved%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20was%20initiated%20because%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20intention%20and%20capacity%20to%20hold%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20as%20per%20its%20constitutional%20mandate%20has%20been%20fading%20fast.%20It%20reached%20a%20nadir%20recently%20when%20the%20Commission%20filed%20a%20counter-affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20containing%20these%20assertions%20which%20are%20alien%20to%20the%20very%20concept%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EECI%20is%20under%20no%20obligation%20to%20cross-verify%20EVMs%20with%20VVPATs%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20VVPAT%20is%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20voter%20can%20verify%20that%20her%20vote%20has%20been%20cast%20as%20intended%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20no%20fundamental%20right%20in%20voters%20to%20verify%20that%20their%20votes%20have%20been%20recorded%20as%20cast%20and%20counted%20as%20recorded%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAny%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20VVPATs%20to%20be%20cross-verified%20will%20pose%20an%20administrative%20challenge%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E100%25%20verification%20of%20VVPAT%20is%20a%20regressive%20step%20and%20takes%20the%20country%20back%20to%20manual%20counting%20of%20ballots%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarlier%20ballot%20counting%20systems%20used%20to%20take%20between%201%20to%206%20days.%20It%20will%20take%20more%20time%20if%20VVPATs%20are%20counted%20and%20recounted%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEVMs%20cannot%20be%20tampered%20with.%20They%20have%20a%20one-time%20programmable%20chip.%20Cannot%20be%20hacked.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECI%20seems%20to%20be%20under%20the%20archaic%20and%20colonial%20belief%20that%20elections%20are%20favours%20bestowed%20on%20the%20people%20of%20India%20and%20not%20instruments%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20sovereignty%20from%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20The%20People%E2%80%9D%20to%20our%20elected%20representatives%20to%20run%20the%20government%20on%20our%20behalf.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20disturbing%20is%20that%20ECI%20has%20been%20falsely%20claiming%20that%20the%20EVM%20(BU-VVPAT-CU)%20units%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20standalone%20machines%20having%20one-time%20programmable%20chips.%E2%80%9D%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20name%20and%20symbols%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20to%20EVM%20using%20an%20external%20device%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20finalisation%20of%20the%20candidate%20list.%C2%A0%20ECI%20Manual%20itself%20states%20at%208.4.2%20that%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20engineers%20are%20to%20use%20a%20device%20called%20Symbol%20Loading%20Unit%20(SLU)%20to%20electronically%20upload%20these%20details%20to%20the%20VVPAT.%20The%20same%20Manual%20in%208.4.4%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20devices%20need%20not%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20strong%20room%20along%20with%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20and%20are%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20engineers%20immediately%20after%20the%20poll%20thus%20making%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20Returning%20Officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20of%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20to%20an%20external%20device%20not%20maintained%20within%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20Returning%20Officers%2FDistrict%20Election%20Officers%20after%20election%20is%20announced%2C%20candidate%20sequence%20is%20firmed%20up%2C%20and%20second%20randomisation%20and%20booth%20allotment%20of%20EVMs%20finalised%20makes%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20practices%20in%20conducting%20elections%20extremely%20suspect.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20voting%20and%20counting%20to%20insider%2Foutsider%20manipulation%20with%20ECI%20being%20a%20party%20to%20it.%20This%20cannot%20be%20countenanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-indias-elections-free-and-fair%5C%22%3EAre%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%20Free%20and%20Fair%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20actual%20voting%20process%2C%20a%20voter%20presses%20the%20ballot%20button%20opposite%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20of%20his%2Fher%20choice%20on%20the%20EVM%20and%20will%20hear%20a%20beep%20sound.%20A%20slip%20appears%20in%20the%20transparent%20window%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine.%20The%20slip%20with%20the%20Candidate%20serial%20No.%2C%20Name%20and%20Symbol%20are%20visible%20for%207%20seconds%20before%20they%20drop%20in%20the%20sealed%20VVPAT%20box.%20The%20slip%20is%20too%20small%20to%20handle%2C%20printed%20on%20thermal%20paper%20and%20evaporates%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks%2Fmonths.%20This%20is%20suspect%20and%20non-transparent.%20A%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20in%20his%2Fher%20hand%20and%20cast%20it%20in%20a%20chip-free%20ballot%20box%20for%20the%20vote%20to%20be%20valid.%C2%A0%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20larger%20in%20size%20and%20must%20be%20printed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20cannot%20be%20altered%20and%20can%20be%20preserved%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20votes%20recorded%20in%20the%20EVM%20is%20counted%20by%20pressing%20the%20appropriate%20button%20marked%20%E2%80%9CResult%E2%80%9D%20provided%20in%20the%20Control%20Unit%20whereby%20the%20total%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20polled%20by%20each%20candidate%20are%20displayed%20in%20respect%20of%20each%20such%20candidate%20on%20the%20display%20panel%20provided%20for%20the%20purpose%20in%20the%20unit.%20Corresponding%20entries%20made%20in%20a%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20and%20the%20particulars%20so%20entered%20in%20the%20result%20sheet%20is%20announced.%20Rule%2056D(4)(b)%20of%20the%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20(Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202013%20provides%20for%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20count%20over%20the%20electronic%20tally%20of%20ballots%20cast%20and%20calculated%20on%20the%20EVMs.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20that%20should%20be%20fully%20counted%20for%20all%20constituencies%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20any%20candidate%2C%20or%20in%20his%20absence%2C%20his%20election%20agent%20or%20any%20of%20his%20counting%20agents%20may%20apply%20in%20writing%20to%20the%20returning%20officer%20to%20count%20the%20printed%20paper%20slips%20in%20the%20drop%20box%20of%20the%20printer%20in%20respect%20of%20any%20polling%20station%20or%20polling%20stations.%20On%20such%20application%20being%20made%2C%20the%20returning%20officer%20shall%20decide%20the%20matter%20and%20may%20allow%20the%20application%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%20or%20may%20reject%20in%20whole%2C%20if%20it%20appears%20to%20him%20to%20be%20frivolous%20or%20unreasonable.%20This%20is%20a%20highly%20arbitrary%20and%20undemocratic%20process%20which%20can%20be%20brazenly%20misused%2Fabused%20by%20election%20officials%20under%20political%20pressure%20as%20has%20been%20happening.%20The%20correct%20process%20is%20to%20count%20only%20VVPAT%20slips.%20If%20needed%2C%20results%20of%20the%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20could%20be%20cross-verified%20with%20the%20electronic%20tallies%20of%20the%20EVMs%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%20In%20case%20of%20any%20mismatch%2C%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20the%20final%20result.%20Forms%2017A%20(Register%20of%20Electors)%20and%20Forms%2017C%20(Account%20of%20votes%20recorded)%20must%20be%20tallied%20with%20the%20manual%20count%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20before%20the%20declaration%20of%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20essential%20aspects%20of%20Electoral%20Democracy%2C%20which%20are%20well%20within%20the%20remit%20of%20the%20ECI%20and%20are%20doable%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20are%20the%20demands%20contained%20in%20the%20public%20petition%20to%20the%20ECI%20which%20the%20Commission%20refuses%20even%20to%20acknowledge%20obviously%20under%20directions%20from%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20who%20are%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20current%20flawed%20and%20undemocratic%20system.%20In%20the%20event%20is%20it%20not%20the%20duty%20and%20responsibility%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20take%20up%20this%20issue%20vigorously%20to%20ensure%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20with%20integrity%3F%20But%20so%20far%20INDIA%20Block%20has%20failed%20in%20their%20duty%20while%20in%20our%20neighbouring%20small%20countries-Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh-EVMs%20have%20been%20discarded%20because%20of%20joint%20action%20by%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20bloc%20should%20realise%20that%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Celection%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%E2%80%9D%20have%20become%20synonymous.%20As%20of%20now%20the%20only%20way%20to%20choose%20our%20representatives%20to%20govern%20ourselves%20is%20through%20the%20electoral%20process.%20%E2%80%9CResolving%20to%20fight%20authoritarianism%20with%20full%20might%20to%20defend%20Democracy%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20noble%20thing%20to%20do.%20But%20it%20should%20start%20with%20ensuring%20the%20fairness%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20Block%20to%20defend%20India%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20would%20become%20a%20question%20mark.%20And%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20this%20could%20be%20disastrous!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703938034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FVVPAT-machine-PIB.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commission-must-recognise-vvpat-paper-trail-is-central-to-infusing-trust-in-evms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20demand%20for%20this%20in%20a%20resolution%20was%20initiated%20by%20civil%20society%20in%20August%20because%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20intention%20and%20capacity%20to%20hold%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20as%20per%20its%20constitutional%20mandate%20has%20been%20fading%20fast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commission-must-recognise-vvpat-paper-trail-is-central-to-infusing-trust-in-evms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Neel%3A'Dunki%20vs%20Salaar'%20clash%20is%20nasty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703936578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106403895%2Cimgsize-40372.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffilmmaker-prashanth-neel-urges-respect-for-shah-rukh-khan-and-prabhas-amidst-nasty-dunki-vs-salaar-clash%2Farticleshow%2F106403948.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106403948.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDirector%20Prashanth%20Neel%20addresses%20the%20rivalry%20between%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20fans%20and%20Prabhas'%20fans%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20more%20respectful%20narrative.%20He%20emphasizes%20that%20the%20box%20office%20clash%20between%20'Salaar'%20and%20'Dunki'%20is%20not%20a%20cinematic%20war%20but%20a%20fight%20for%20survival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2