%2Ftennis%2F67847517.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20Years%20After%20Announcement%2C%20Soren%20Govt%20Yet%20to%20Withdraw%20Cases%20Pending%20Against%20Pathalgadi%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F22171455%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-22-at-3.48.58-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFive%20cases%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Pathalgadi%20movement%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Kunti%20district%20are%20still%20pending%20to%20be%20withdrawn.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20current%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20took%20over%2C%20he%20vowed%20to%20withdraw%20all%20cases%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20movement%2C%20filed%20under%20his%20predecessor%20Raghubar%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%2021%20cases%20registered%20by%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20Khunti%2C%2016%20so%20far%20have%20been%20withdrawn%20under%20the%20Soren%20government.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20the%20Soren%20government%20going%20against%20its%20promise%20filed%20a%20new%20case%20against%20the%20movement.%20The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20regarding%20pending%20cases%20has%20been%20disclosed%20by%20replies%20received%20to%20appeals%20filed%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%2C%20said%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2029%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Soren%20right%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704003291869000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3j-rVqc82fALGEMexM9eft%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases%2C%20it%20was%20met%20with%20widespread%20appreciation%20and%20support.%20The%20earlier%20Jharkhand%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Das%2C%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Pathalgadi%C2%A0movement%20and%20responded%20with%20severe%20violence%20and%20repression.%20It%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20the%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20movement%20and%20also%20several%20Adivasi%20traditional%20heads%20of%20the%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20about%20200%20named%20accused%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20unnamed%20people%20under%20charges%20that%20included%20abetment%2C%20obstruction%20to%20public%20servants%20discharging%20their%20duty%2C%20creation%20of%20public%20nuisance%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20and%20even%20sedition.%20As%20many%20as%2028%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20related%20to%20the%20P%3Cspan%3Eathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%20were%20spread%20across%20Khunti%20(21)%2C%20Saraikela-Kharsawan%20(5)%2C%20and%20West%20Singhbhum%20(2)%20districts%20were%20registered%20by%20the%20Raghubar%20Das%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20Soren%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20raised%20during%20the%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20widespread%20violation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20(PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20etc.)%2C%20marginalisation%20of%20Adivasi%20worldview%2C%20exploitation%20of%20Adivasis%20by%20the%20police%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20non-Adivasis%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20Soren%20government%20to%20immediately%20withdraw%20all%20