ed%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERafaqat%20says%20that%20to%20date%20there%20has%20been%20no%20progress%20in%20his%20brother%E2%80%99s%20case.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%20never%20consumed%20any%20poison.%20We%20were%20told%20over%20the%20phone%20that%20he%20was%20lying%20unconscious%20on%20the%20road%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital.%20They%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20caught%20anyone%20responsible%20for%20the%20wounds%20on%20my%20dead%20brother%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rafaqat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoonch-civilians-killed-are-among-the-men-seen-in-video-being-tortured-by-soldiers-sarpanch-confirms%5C%22%3EPoonch%20Civilians%20Killed%20Are%20Among%20the%20Men%20Seen%20in%20Video%20Being%20Tortured%20By%20Soldiers%2C%20Sarpanch%20Confirms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20around%20the%20time%20that%20the%20case%20was%20fresh%20that%20the%20family%20was%20assured%20justice%20and%20action%2C%20says%20Rafaqat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20sought%20a%20judicial%20probe%20into%20the%20death%20of%20Mukhtar%2C%20while%20also%20alleging%20that%20the%20order%20of%20the%20magisterial%20inquiry%20reads%20more%20like%20%E2%80%9Can%20attempt%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20truth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20in%20Poonch%20reminded%20me%20of%20what%20my%20brother%20saw.%20These%20deaths%20are%20of%20the%20same%20pattern.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20they%20were%20hellbent%20to%20pass%20off%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20death%20as%20suicide%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rafaqat%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98We%20feel%20betrayed%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20four%20years%20since%20they%20killed%20our%20children%2C%20but%20these%20recent%20killings%20triggered%20our%20pain%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammad%20Yusuf%2C%20father%20of%2024-year-old%20Ibrar%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20alongside%20Imtiyaz%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20heard%20the%20news%20about%20the%20custodial%20killings%20in%20Poonch%2C%20I%20could%20only%20think%20of%20how%20the%20remaining%20families%20would%20feel%20as%20dead%20as%20I%20did%20when%20they%20killed%20my%20Ibrar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yusuf%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYusuf%20also%20remarked%20that%20being%20a%20part%20of%20a%20community%20that%20lived%20in%20the%20border%20districts%2C%20they%20have%20had%20loved%20ones%20laying%20down%20their%20lives%20to%20protect%20the%20country%20from%20terrorism%2C%20sometimes%20for%20the%20army%20and%20other%20times%20with%20the%20army.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20such%20incidents%20continue%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20love%20that%20the%20community%20has%20will%20start%20turning%20into%20hate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20Muslim%20from%20Pakistan%20illegally%20enters%20our%20border%2C%20we%20never%20treat%20them%20as%20Muslim%2C%20we%20deal%20with%20them%20as%20outsiders%20trying%20to%20mess%20with%20the%20peace%20of%20our%20beloved%20country.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20get%3F%20They%20murdered%20our%20children%20with%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20these%20boys%20killed%20in%20Poonch%20were%20treated%20worse%20than%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yusuf%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20their%20loved%20one%20is%20unbearable%20to%20live%20with%2C%20they%20say%20that%20the%20recent%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Famshipora-fake-encounter-case-army-captain-life-sentence-suspended-granted-conditional-bail-101699892305601.html%5C%22%3Esuspend%20the%20life%20sentence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20Army%20captain%20who%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20killing%20the%20three%20men%20has%20also%20shaken%20their%20faith%20in%20getting%20justice%20as%20a%20minority%20community%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20same%20is%20Sabir%20Hussain%2C%20father%20of%20Imtiyaz%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20views%20the%20situation%20from%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20grieving%20parent.%20Hussain%20stands%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20son%20and%20the%20other%20two%20killed%20are%20victims%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20encounter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20killed%20our%20sons%20and%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20justice%20for%20us.%20Nobody%20is%20with%20us%20because%20we%20come%20from%20impoverished%20backgrounds.%20He%20should%20have%20been%20hanged%20but%20he%20is%20roaming%20free.%20We%20feel%20cheated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hussain%20complained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20Poonch%20killings%2C%20Hussain%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20someone%20dies%2C%20the%20administration%20comes%20offering%20compensation%20and%20jobs%2C%20but%20these%20families%20should%20not%20believe%20them%2C%20because%20even%20this%20compensation%20is%20a%20test%20in%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20speaks%20of%20getting%20compensation%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccycle%20of%20harassment%E2%80%9D%20since%20he%20claims%20that%20while%20the%20administration%20had%20offered%20Rs%205%20lakh%20cash%20compensation%20to%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20after%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20an%20encounter%20was%20busted%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20%E2%80%93%20this%20compensation%20money%20was%20used%20up%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%20in%20visiting%20the%20government%20offices%20and%20pursuing%20the%20case%20for%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703925773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-families-affected-by-fake-encounters-view-poonch-civilian-deaths-with-doubts-and-despair%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20video%20clip%20showing%20three%20civilians%20before%20they%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Poonch%20m