%E2%80%99s%20report%20have%20been%20done%20away%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20the%20central%20observers%20carried%20a%20sealed%20cover%20which%20contained%20the%20name%20of%20the%20high%20commands%20choice%20for%20the%20chief%20ministership.%20And%20the%20observers%20respectfully%20opened%20it%20and%20declared%20the%20winner.%20The%20sealed%20cover%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20authority%20which%20every%20one%20in%20the%20party%20must%20accept%20without%20grudge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20those%20those%20enjoying%20maximum%20support%20among%20the%20elected%20MLAs%20should%20take%20the%20cake.%20The%20GenX%20BJP%20CMs%20are%20not%20answerable%20to%20MLAs%20or%20their%20electors%20but%20high%20command.%20No%20one%20else.%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20trust%20is%20most%20crucial.%20Otherwise%20you%20lose%20the%20job%20within%20weeks.%20That%20is%20the%20story%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fdata%2Fdata-tirath-singh-rawat-vacates-office-in-less-than-four-months-cms-with-shortest-stints%2Farticle61443832.ece%5C%22%3ETirat%20Singh%20Rawat%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20four-month%20tenure%20as%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20CM%3C%2Fa%3E%20tells%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sealed%20cover%20doctrine%20is%20a%20Gujarat%20model.%20It%20was%20first%20introduced%20when%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20replaced%20Vijay%20Rupani%20as%20chief%20minister%20in%202021.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20CEO-style%20imposition%20had%20become%20the%20norm.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20choice%20of%20the%20new%20CMs%20%E2%80%93%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20and%20Vishudeo%20Sai%20%E2%80%93%20follows%20a%20pattern%3A%20confirmed%20RSS%20background%20with%20tilak%20on%20forehead%2C%20less%20known%20outside%20the%20state%20if%20not%20first%20timers%20and%20with%20little%20following%20in%20the%20state.%20They%20perpetually%20look%20to%20high%20command%20for%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20first%20action%20of%20the%20new%20CMs%20was%20to%20issue%20full-page%20advertisements%20in%20Delhi%20with%20their%20photos%20with%20PM.%20They%20all%20look%20to%20Adityanath%20and%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20as%20role%20models.%20So%20much%20so%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbhopal-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-cm-mohan-yadav-bans-meat-sales-in-open-101702525512937.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMadhya%2520Pradesh%2527s%2520newly%2520appointed%2520chief%2Cfirst%2520cabinet%2520meeting%2520on%2520Wednesday.%26amp%3Btext%3D%25E2%2580%259CAfter%2520the%2520implementation%2520of%2520food%2Cand%2520fish%2520in%2520the%2520open%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20decision%20of%20new%20MP%20cabinet%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20to%20ban%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20eggs%20in%20public%20places%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBulldozers%20roam%20on%20the%20streets%20looking%20for%20the%20right%20targets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20parliament%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20parliament%20is%20the%20latest%20to%20fall%20for%20the%20new%20imperious%20style.%20During%20the%20winter%20session%2C%20a%20record%20number%20of%20146%20opposition%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20100%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%2046%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20suspended.%20During%20the%20Modi%20rule%2C%20expulsions%20and%20suspensions%20in%20parliament%20shot%20up%20by%2071%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%202019%2C%20presiding%20officers%20resorted%20to%20suspensions%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat.%20During%20this%20winter%20session%2C%20every%20day%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Chairman%20drew%20up%20a%20list%20of%20what%20they%20called%20violators%20of%20discipline%20and%20went%20on%20announcing%20the%20names%20of%20MPs%20to%20be%20suspended.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%20in%20one%20case%2C%20name%20of%20a%20MP%20who%20was%20on%20leave%20was%20included.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20suspension%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fsr-parthiban-dmk-mp-suspended-for-lok-sabha-protest-on-sick-leave-9068452%2F%5C%22%3Ewithdrawn%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20error%20was%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20concerned%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20all%20began%20with%20the%20jumping%20of%20two%20youths%20into%20the%20House%20from%20the%20visitors%20gallery%20%E2%80%93%20again%20a%20first%20%E2%80%93%20to%20highlight%20the%20growing%20unemployment.%20To%20heighten%20the%20drama%2C%20the%20youths%20burst%20smoke%20canisters.%20They%20had%20pamphlets%20calling%20PM%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F455447%2F53040909%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3Emissing%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20such%20embarrassing%20details%20were%20played%20down%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20vast%20publicity%20machinery%20and%20the%20mainstream%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20the%20intruders%20were%20charged%20charged%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20while%20the%20the%20BJP%20MP%20who%20issued%20passes%20to%20them%20went%20scot%20free.%20For%2C%20he%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-bjp-mp-pratap-simha-who-gave-lok-sabha-passes-to-intruders-what-he-said-101702517951930.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etilakdhari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20prominent%20%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20background%20of%20%3Cem%3Evibhuti%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20forehead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20demand%20of%20the%20suspended%20opposition%20members%20was%20a%20discussion%20in%20House%20on%20the%20serious%20security%20breach%20happened.%20They%20also%20insisted%20on%20the%20PM%20and%20home%20minister%20come%20to%20the%20House%20to%20explain%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20the%20security%20breach%20happened.%20This%20is%20a%20legitimate%20right%20the%20members%20this%20august%20House%20had%20exercised%20in%20the%20past.%20Presiding%20officers%20have%20generally%20been%20very%20lenient%20on%20such%20protests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20what%20happened%20after%20a%20more%20threatening%20attack%20on%20parliament%20happened%20in%20December%2C%202001.%20The%20opposition%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20insisted%20on%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20House.%20Unlike%20Modi%20and%20Shah%2C%20Vajpayee%20and%20home%20minister%20L.K.%20Advani%20readily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F455457%2F5533014%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3Ecame%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F455457%2F5533014%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3Eto%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F455457%2F5533014%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3Ethe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F455457%2F5533014%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3EHouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gave%20an%20account%20of%20the%20line%20of%20investigations%20into%20attack.%20The%20government%20side%20also%20allowed%20a%20short%20duration%20discussion%20in%20both%20Houses.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20parliament%20remained%20paralysed%20for%20weeks%20together%20when%20BJP%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20coal%20allocations.%20Such%20expressions%20of%20dissent%20were%20always%20viewed%20as%20legitimate%20mode%20of%20expressing%20democratic%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20senior%20ministers%20of%20the%20Modi%20cabinet%20%E2%80%93%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20and%20Arun%20Jaitely%20%E2%80%93%20had%20in%20the%20past%20forcefully%20disagreed%20with%20what%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Dhankhar%20now%20describe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fparliament-gridlock-democracy-bjp-8057195%2F%5C%22%3Eviolation%20of%20parliamentary%20discipline%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20September%207%2C%202012%2C%20Swaraj%20had%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNot%20allowing%20Parliament%20to%20function%20is%20a%20form%20of%20democratic%20protest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaitely%2C%20senior%20minister%20and%20close%20aide%20of%20Modi%20even%20when%20L.K.%20Advani%20was%20in%20contest%20for%20the%20prime%20ministership%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Parliament%20is%20used%20to%20ignore%20issues%E2%80%A6%20parliamentary%20obstruction%20is%20not%20undemocratic.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Jaitely%20said%20so%20at%20Ranchi%20on%20January%2030%2C%202011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20late%20colleagues%20of%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20were%20simply%20reiterating%20the%20existing%20the%20parliamentary%20traditions.%20Disruptions%20have%20never%20considered%20as%20a%20punishable%20offence%20deserving%20suspensions.%20It%20is%20a%20pernicious%20practice%20now%20being%20imposed%20by%20the%20two%20incumbent%20presiding%20officers.%20Apparently%2C%20parliamentary%20management%20has%20become%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20Modi%20project%20to%20perpetuate%20a%20system%20of%20duopoly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20political%20thinker%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%20describes%20as%20%E2%80%98India%E2%80%99s%20monumental%20tragedy.%E2%80%99%20Parliament%20as%20an%20institution%20of%20functioning%20democracy%20is%20effectively%20dead%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-parliamentary-democracy-bharat-india-mps-suspension-9077660%2F%5C%22%3Ehe%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cs