0alarming%C2%A0%20This%20week%2C%20the%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhalf-of-the-bills-passed-debated-for-less-than-2-hrs-each-report-9079717%2F%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20about%20half%20of%20the%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20were%20cleared%20after%20less%20than%20two%20hours%E2%80%99%20discussion.%20Only%2016%25%20were%20referred%20to%20standing%20committees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20bills%20referred%20to%20standing%20committees%20came%20down%20from%2072%25%20during%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20just%2016%25%20during%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20No%20bill%20was%20referred%20to%20House%20committees%20this%20winter%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20EC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20was%20the%20next%20in%20line%20of%20fire.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20election%20commissioners%2C%20including%20the%20CEC%2C%20were%20appointed%20by%20a%20three-member%20panel%20consisting%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20opposition%20nominee%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20The%20system%20was%20introduced%20following%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20bill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcji-dropped-from-cec-selection-panel-centre-defends-bill-says-supreme-court-ruling-is-followed-11703173327015.html%5C%22%3Epassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20during%20the%20winter%20session%20excludes%20the%20CJI%20from%20the%20panel.%20The%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20position%20will%20be%20filled%20a%20minister%20nominated%20by%20the%20PM.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20Modi%20has%20an%20assured%20majority%20in%20the%20three-member%20selection%20panel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20prompted%20the%20retired%20Justice%20Rohington%20F%20Nariman%2C%20a%20former%20solicitor