%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offending%20reports%20had%20brought%20out%20several%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20Dwarka%20Expressway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decline%20of%20CAG%20under%20Modi%20has%20been%20really%20disheartening.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fgovernment%252Fvery-low-number-of-cag-reports-tables-in-parliament-in-2023%2Bcag.%26rlz%3D1C9BKJA_enIN883IN883%26oq%3D%26aqs%3Dchrome.8.69i176j69i59i450l9.438499j1j7%26hl%3Den-US%26sourceid%3Dchrome-mobile%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20showed%20that%20the%20number%20of%20reports%20averaged%2022%20between%202019%20and%202023.%20During%20the%20pre-Modi%20days%20it%20was%20as%20high%20as%2040.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20broad%20position%20as%20far%20as%20the%20checks%20and%20balances%20to%20unbridled%20executive%20power%20envisaged%20by%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20are%20concerned.%20In%20sum%2C%20there%20is%20no%20obstacle%20to%20the%20abuse%20of%20authority.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20accomplished%20all%20this%20in%20less%20than%20two%20terms%20%E2%80%93%20ten%20years%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20now%20hoping%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%20If%20he%20succeeds%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20more%20pillars%20left%20to%20crumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EP.%20Raman%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703902921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F28144222%2FIMG_0206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-cag-ec-more-pillars-crumble-as-modi-tightens-hold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20fall%20as%20an%20institution%20of%20functioning%20democracy%20was%20accompanied%20by%20axe%20