0fill%20virtually%20every%20corner%20and%20crevice%20of%20the%20year%20ahead.%20The%20first%20of%20the%20primaries%20and%20caucuses%20which%20select%20the%20candidates%20of%20the%20two%20main%20parties%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20mid-west%20state%20of%20Iowa%20in%20mid-January.%20Then%20the%20electioneering%20is%20never-ending%20%E2%80%93%20I%20promise%2C%20it%20really%20will%20feel%20like%20that%20%E2%80%93%20right%20through%20to%20the%20Presidential%20election%20on%20November%204.%20The%20winner%20is%20sworn-in%20on%20January%2020%2C%202025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%20big%20three%20voting%20in%20the%20coming%20year%2C%20the%20US%20contest%20is%20by%20far%20the%20most%20uncertain.%20Who%20knows%20what%20will%20happen%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20election%20%E2%80%93%20but%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20change%20in%20governing%20party%2C%20that%20would%20really%20be%20a%20shock.%C2%A0%20In%20Britain%2C%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20change%20in%20governing%20party%2C%20that%20would%20be%20an%20even%20bigger%20surprise%20%E2%80%93%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20Conservatives%20appear%20to%20have%20an%20electoral%20death%20wish%2C%20and%20after%20fourteen%20years%20in%20the%20wilderness%20the%20Labour%20Party%20is%20set%20to%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20contest%20taking%20shape%20in%20America%20is%20both%20unappetisingly%20stale%20and%20effervescently%20unpredictable.%20Stale%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20re-run%20of%20the%20last%20election%20four%20years%20ago.%20In%20November%2C%20the%20odds%20are%20that%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%2081-year-old%20incumbent%20will%20face%20off%20against%20the%20man%20he%20narrowly%20evicted%20from%20office%20in%202020%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20will%20by%20then%20be%2078.%20The%20polls%20point%20to%20a%20tight%20result%2C%20with%20Trump%20slightly%20better%20placed%20to%20win.%20It%20will%20be%20brutal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmerican%20politics%20feels%20to%20be%20a%20battle%20between%20two%20rival%20dynasties%20in%20which%20ageing%20patriarchs%20are%20clinging%20to%20power%2C%20seeing%20off%20all%20attempts%20to%20install%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leaders.%20Much%20of%20the%20contest%20will%20not%20be%20about%20policies%2C%20but%20about%20whether%20the%20presidential%20candidates%20retain%20the%20mental%20acumen%20and%20physical%20stamina%20required%20of%20our%20planet%E2%80%99s%20most%20powerful%20leader.%20You%20can%20see%20why%20the%20Economist%20Intelligence%20Unit%E2%80%99s%20Democracy%20Index%20classifies%20America%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98flawed%20democracy%E2%80%99%20(the%20same%20label%20it%20applies%20to%20India%2C%20just%20by%20the%20way).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20concept%20of%20liberal%20democracy%20is%20in%20some%20disrepair%20in%20much%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20because%20some%20of%20our%20principal%20democracies%20have%20lost%20the%20knack%20of%20political%20renewal.%20And%20because%20some%20of%20those%20who%20stand%20for%20election%20are%20at%20heart%20neither%20liberal%20nor%20democrats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20even%20political%20systems%20which%20are%20not%20at%20all%20pluralist%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20go%20through%20the%20charade%20of%20an%20election.%20President%20Putin%20is%20standing%20again%20as%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20president%20in%20March.%20I%20hear%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20favourite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20feast%20of%20other%20contests%20around%20the%20world%2C%20enough%20to%20keep%20psephologists%20%E2%80%93%20the%20folks%20that%20make%20a%20special%20study%20of%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20at%20full%20stretch.%20Bangladesh%20holds%20Parliamentary%20elections%20in%20early%20January%3B%20Pakistan%20is%20due%20to%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20the%20following%20month%3B%20Indonesia%20also%20votes%20in%20February%3B%20Mexico%E2%80%99s%20general%20election%20is%20due%20in%20June%3B%20and%20we%20will%20also%20have%20polling%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20a%20presidential%20election%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDozens%20of%20other%20contests%20are%20scheduled%2C%20from%20Iceland%20to%20Moldova%2C%20from%20Taiwan%20to%20Tuvalu.%20More%20than%20seventy%20countries%20will%20hold%20nationwide%20elections%20of%20some%20sort.%20Some%20of%20these%20will%20be%20tolerably%20free%20and%20fair%3B%20at%20least%20as%20many%20will%20be%20marred%20by%20restrictions%20on%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20association%20and%20an%20absence%20of%20effective%20oversight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll-in-all%2C%202024%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20election%20year%20there%E2%80%99s%20ever%20been.%20Fingers%20crossed!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Ffrino%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Whitehead%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20honorary%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20a%20former%20BBC%20India%20Correspondent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703872399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29232232%2FUntitled-design-17-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiggest-election-year-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%2070%20countries%20will%20hold%20nationwide%20elections%20of%20some%20sort.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbiggest-election-year-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Flamin'%20Hot'%20Doritos%20and%20Cheetos%20seasoning%20sparks%20workplace%20safety%20complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703871960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-adelaide-pepsico-smiths-sn