public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Paswan%20(6%2C943%2C000%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Paswans%20or%20Dusadhs%20%E2%80%93%20named%20so%20because%20of%20their%20headstrong%20nature%20%E2%80%93%20are%20considered%20untouchable%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20castes%20and%20also%20treated%20with%20antipathy%20by%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20communities.%20%3Cspan%3E%20While%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20specific%20enmity%20with%20Yadavs%2C%20Koeris%20and%20Kurmis%2C%20but%20a%20certain%20antagonism%20exists%20between%20these%20groups%20and%20the%20Paswans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20can%20come%20across%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20working%20as%20watchmen%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echowkidars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20areas%20of%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPaswans%20have%20worked%20as%20agricultural%20labourers.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20are%20landless%20and%20lack%20resources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20members%20of%20the%20Pasi%20caste%2C%20they%20also%20extract%20toddy%20from%20palm%20trees.%20The%20process%20involves%20climbing%20a%20palm%20tree%20and%20carefully%20peeling%20its%20shoots%20until%20toddy%20oozes%20out.%20A%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20Pasis%20and%20Paswans%20is%20that%20the%20former%20primarily%20depend%20on%20palm%20trees%20for%20their%20livelihood%20while%20the%20latter%20also%20work%20with%20leather%2C%20and%20are%20hunters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBritish%20ethnographer%20and%20historian%20Herbert%20Hope%20Risley%20has%20described%20Paswans%20as%20an%20agrarian%20caste%20in%20his%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Tribes%20and%20Castes%20of%20Bengal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1891).%20Bihar%20was%20then%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Presidency%20and%20according%20to%20Risley%2C%20Paswans%20inhabited%20the%20areas%20of%20Chhotanagpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20some%20more%20information%20about%20them%20in%20the%20history%20recorded%20by%20the%20British.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20the%20British%20came%20to%20India%20and%20encountered%20Siraj%20ud-Daula%2C%20the%20last%20independent%20Nawab%20of%20Bengal%2C%20they%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group.%20The%20British%20transformed%20their%20status%20from%20being%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20to%20soldiers%20who%20exhibited%20courage.%20Something%20similar%20had%20happened%20in%201818%20when%20the%20British%20deployed%20Mahar%20caste%20members%20as%20soldiers%20and%20won%20the%20battle%20of%20Bhima-Koregaon%20against%20the%20Peshwas.%20Prior%20to%20this%20change%2C%20Paswan%20used%20to%20be%20the%20w%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eatchmen%20of%20Bhumihars%20and%20Brahmins.%20The%20British%20recognised%20their%20capabilities%20and%20with%20their%20help%2C%20they%20defeated%20the%20Nawab%20in%20the%20Battle%20of%20Plassey%20in%201757.%20In%20the%20battle%2C%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Paswan%20caste%20had%20fought%20for%20Robert%20Clive%E2%80%99s%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEndless%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20Hinduise%20Paswans%20who%20originally%20belonged%20to%20a%20tribal%20community.%20One%20proof%20is%20offered%20by%20Badri%20Narayan%20in%20his%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDocumenting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDissent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%202013.%20According%20to%20Narayan%2C%20Paswan%20are%20a%20warrior%20caste%20and%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20they%20were%20once%20one%20of%20the%2022%20branches%20of%20%E2%80%98Gehlot%E2%80%99%20of%20Rajasthan.%20Narayan%20describes%20them%20as%20those%20who%20fought%20against%20the%20Mughals%20and%20also%20claims%20that%20after%20being%20defeated%2C%20they%20fled%20to%20the%20eastern%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Narayan%20does%20not%20explain%20why%20the%20Rajput%20rulers%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20who%20were%20also%20defeated%20by%20the%20Mughals%2C%20did%20not%20flee%20the%20region.%20Does%20he%20want%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20Rajputs%20compromised%20with%20the%20Mughals%20while%20the%20Paswans%20preserved%20their%20self-respect%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubhadra%20Mitra%20Channa%20and%20John%20P.%20Mencher%20in%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELife%20as%20a%20Dalit%3A%20Views%20from%20the%20Bottom%20on%20the%20Caste%20in%20India%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3En%20page%20322-323)%20have%20referred%20to%20Paswans%20as%20Kshatriya.%20They%20are%20probably%20correct%20since%20in%20the%20past%2C%20%E2%80%98Kshatriya%E2%80%99%20used%20to%20mean%20%E2%80%98regional%20heroes.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20folk%20heroes%20of%20Paswan%20caste%20have%20also%20been%20Hinduised%2C%20like%20the%20folk%20hero%2C%20Chauharmal.%20The%20story%20of%20Chauharmal%20and%20Reshma%20bears%20resemblance%20to%20the%20famous%20stories%20of%20Heer-Ranjha%20and%20Romeo-Juliet.%20This%20folk%20tale%20is%20orally%20recited%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20Mokama%20district%20of%20Bihar%20even%20today.%20Another%20such%20folk%20hero%2C%20Salhesh%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20northern%20region%20of%20Ganga%2C%20is%20known%20as%20a%20kind%20ruler.%20But%20Pandit%20Pradeep%20Jha%20in%20his%20book%20linked%20him%20along%20with%20the%20Paswans%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20described%20them%20as%20the%20descendants%20of%20Dushasan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Paswan%20caste%20group%20are%20spread%20mainly%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20caste%20group%20has%20a%20sizeable%20population%20especially%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Banaras%2C%20Chandauli%2C%20Sonbhadra%2C%20Mirzapur%2C%20Ghazipur%2C%20Ballia%2C%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Deoria%2C%20Siddharthnagar%2C%20Basti%2C%20Bahraich%2C%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%2C%20Mau%2C%20Jaunpur%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Azamgarh%20etc.%20whereas%20in%20Bihar%2C%20they%20mostly%20live%20in%20Araria%2C%20Arwal%2C%20Aurangabad%2C%20Banka%2C%20Begusarai%2C%20Bhabua%2C%20Bhagalpur%2C%20Bhojpur%2C%20Buxar%2C%20Darbhanga%2C%20East%20Champaran%2C%20Gaya%2C%20Gopalganj%2C%20Jamui%2C%20Jehanabad%2C%20Katihar%2C%20Khagaria%2C%20Kishanganj%2C%20Lakhisarai%2C%20Munger%2C%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Nawada%2C%20Patna%2C%20Purnia%2C%20Rohtas%2C%20Saharsa%2C%20Samastipur%2C%20Saran%2C%20Shekhar%2C%20Shikhapura%2C%20Sitamarhi%2C%20Siwan%2C%20Supaul%2C%20Vaishali%2C%20and%20West%20Champaran.%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20they%20mostly%20reside%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Lohardaga%2C%20Gumla%2C%20Simdega%2C%20Palamu%2C%20West%20Singhbhum%2C%20Seraikela%2C%20Kharsawan%2C%20East%20Singhbhum%2C%20Dumka%2C%20Jamtara%2C%20Sahebganj%2C%20Pakur%2C%20Godda%2C%20Hazaribagh%2C%20Chatra%2C%20Koderma%2C%20Giridih%2C%20Dhanbad%2C%20Bokaro%20and%20Deoghar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20almost%20every%20state%2C%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20They%20are%20one%20of%20those%20Scheduled%20Castes%20who%20organised%20and%20empowered%20themselves%20the%20most%20after%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20constitution%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Paswan%20population%20is%206%2C943%2C000%20which%20is%205.311%25%20of%20the%20total%20population.%20It%20is%20a%20considerable%20size%20for%20a%20Dalit%20caste.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20political%20influence%20of%20this%20population%20was%20such%20that%20Bhola%20Paswan%20Shastri%2C%20a%20member%20of%20this%20caste%2C%20became%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar.%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20is%20another%20example.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F262741%2Fbihar-caste-survey-paswan-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-