in%20Meghalaya%20%E2%80%94%20like%20fiddlehead%20ferns%2C%20elephant%20apple%2C%20elephant%20foot%20yams%2C%20purple%20yams%2C%20Indian%20sorrel%2C%20fish%20mint%20leaves%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohiong%3C%2Fem%3E%20(blackberry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohplhang%20(%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20root%20vegetable)%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20makes%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20ingredients%20like%20brinjal%20and%20dry%20fish%2C%20fermented%20fish%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20dried%20roselle%20with%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Epura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rice%20flour)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejadoh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20%3Cem%3EKhasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20rice%20recipe)%2C%20beef%20trotter%20soup%2C%20muskmelon%20and%20pork%20gravy%20dish%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20was%20appreciated%20by%20many%2C%20she%20also%20faced%20vicious%20trolling%20and%20hate.%20Trolls%20ridiculed%20her%20for%20cooking%20outdoors%2C%20the%20food%20she%20cooked%2C%20and%20even%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20wore%20slippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20really%20harsh%20comments.%20People%20said%20things%20like%20%E2%80%9CYour%20food%20looks%20like%20dog%20food%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20wearing%20those%20slippers%3F%E2%80%9D.%20I%20cook%20outside%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20electricity%20most%20of%20the%20time%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20our%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trolling%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20she%20considered%20quitting%20social%20media%20due%20to%20the%20excessive%20negativity.%20All%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20was%20showcase%20her%20home%2C%20surroundings%20and%20food.%20Realising%20that%20she%20would%20let%20the%20naysayers%20win%20if%20she%20gave%20up%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20overcome%20the%20hate%20by%20growing%20a%20thick%20skin.%20She%20focused%20on%20the%20positive%20comments%2C%20which%20were%20also%20many%20in%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20accept%20that%2