india.com%2F271527%2Fcentury-old-vadilal-ice-cream-brand-first-to-launch-dollies-cones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20the%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sodas%20but%20it%20was%20his%20son%20Ranchod%20Lal%20Gandhi%20who%20introduced%20ice%20creams%20to%20the%20brand.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20the%20company%20had%20opened%20four%20outlets%20across%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20company%20clocked%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C%20071%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fjaswantiben-popat-lijjat-papad-owner-story-1700660151.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Parle-G%20to%20Lijjat%20Papad%2C%20these%20iconic%20food%20businesses%20of%20India%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20and%20inspiring%20stories%20that%20led%20to%20their%20success%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334682%2Flegacy-food-businesses-nilon-parle-g-balaji-wafers-ravalgaon-multicrore%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Droughts%20Led%20to%20Losses%2C%20Oyster%20Pearl%20Farming%20Helped%20Marathwada%20Farmers%20Reap%20Huge%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertain%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20irrigation%20canals%20completely%20drying%20up%2C%20cultivation%20in%20the%20parched%20land%20of%20the%20Osmanabad%20district%20has%20become%20exhausting%20for%20farmers.%20Lying%20under%20the%20rain%20shadow%20region%20of%20Marathwada%2C%20the%20district%20faces%20acute%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20input%20costs%20and%20unfair%20market%20prices%20have%20severely%20affected%20the%20output%20and%20yield%20of%20the%20major%20crops%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20like%20soybean%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20millet.%20The%20compounding%20debts%20put%20Maharashtra%20farmers%20under%20a%20huge%20economic%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20recurring%20droughts%20force%20farmers%20to%20sometimes%20end%20their%20lives.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F169599016203ADSI-2021Chapter-2Suicides-ExcludingFarmerCauses.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCRB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20data%3C%2Fem%3E%20revealed%20that%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C881%20persons%20involved%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20With%2037.3%20percent%2C%20Maharashtra%20accounted%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20farmer%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20impoverished%20farmers%20have%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20oyster%20pearls%20in%20the%20water-starved%20Marathwada%20to%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20recurring%20droughts%20and%20low%20crop%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20farmer%20is%20Sanjay%20Narsing%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20nine%20other%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20harvested%208%2C000%20pearls%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20pond%2C%20earning%20them%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229545%2Fagra-woman-entrepreneur-grow-oysters-pearl-farming-home-earn-lakhs-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoyster%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads